-- Chapter 574: THE ORD CLASSES -- how one comparison grew three coherent
-- views, why a decidable equality earns a class of its own, and how the
-- rational order crosses the quotient on positive scaling alone, never on
-- cancellation.
--
-- THE THREE VIEWS ARGUMENT. A total order can be presented three ways, and a
-- mature library refuses to choose. The decidable Bool test `le : A -> A ->
-- Bool` COMPUTES -- it is what a runtime branch wants. The three-way
-- `compare : A -> A -> Ordering` folds the two directions of `le` into one
-- verdict (lt, eq, gt), the shape a sort or a search tree wants so it does not
-- re-test the reverse. The erased proof-side `Le A o a b` is the PROPOSITION
-- `Eq Bool (leOf A o a b) true`, the thing a theorem quantifies over. These
-- are not three unrelated notions: `compare` and `le` are inter-derivable
-- (`compareFromLe`, `leFromCompare`), and `Le` is `le` reflected into Prop.
-- The campaign keeps all three COHERENT and puts the two computational ones --
-- `le` AND `compare` -- inside the same ops record, so an instance ships a
-- compare that need not re-run le twice. That is computational prudence, not
-- redundancy: leaving compare out would force every consumer to rebuild it
-- from le at each call, and leaving le out would forbid the cheap single
-- branch. The proof-side `Le` stays OUTSIDE the record (it is derivable and
-- erased), exactly as the algebra hierarchy keeps its laws outside the ops.
--
-- THE OPS / LAWS SPLIT. This chapter mirrors the algebra hierarchy's discipline
-- EXACTLY. An ops class is a Sigma-record of operations (`Ord A` = le then
-- compare); the laws are a SEPARATE And-chain record (`OrdLaws A o` = the six
-- total-order slots leRefl / leTrans / leAntisym / leTotal / cmpEq / cmpLe).
-- The guarded tier -- a decidable order with no proof -- is just the ops record
-- WITHOUT the laws value, so a carrier that can compare but cannot yet prove
-- its order still registers an `Ord` instance. The positional Sigma discipline
-- is the one hazard: an ops class is distinguished by the POSITION and TYPE of
-- its fields, so a new class whose field sequence matches an existing one
-- COLLIDES on hash. `Ord` is a two-field record (le, compare) and is safe; the
-- delicate one is DecEq, below. TestTowerClassHashesDistinct is the standing
-- gate.
--
-- DECEQ, A PRINCIPLED STANDALONE CLASS. Decidable equality is not order. A type
-- can carry a computable `eqb : A -> A -> Bool` with its soundness and
-- reflexivity laws and yet have no sensible `<=`; conversely an order gives an
-- equality only through antisymmetry. So `DecEq` is its own ops class -- the
-- eqb operation IS the payload -- with its own laws record `DecEqLaws`
-- (soundness: eqb reflects propositional equality; reflexivity: eqb a a is
-- true). The subtlety is the hash. A bare `A -> A -> Bool` is STRUCTURALLY
-- identical to `Ord`'s le field and to every other binary-Bool op class, so a
-- naked function type would collide. `DecEq A` therefore WRAPS the operation in
-- a Sig with a Bool phantom-marker second field (value `true`), exactly as
-- `Semiring` is a record and not a bare tuple. The marker is Bool, not a fresh
-- nullary datatype, because a new single-nullary-constructor type would risk
-- the one-nullary-ctor collision. DecEq's Sig then differs from Ord's in the
-- SECOND family (constantly Bool vs A -> A -> Ordering), so the two are
-- distinct, and the audit confirms it against the whole tower.
--
-- THE TOWER INSTANCES. Whole is the base: `decEqWhole` is `eqW`, `ordWhole` is
-- `leb` with `compareFromLe` on top, and the six laws are the leb corpus read
-- off the nose (`Le Whole ordWhole a b` computes to `Eq Bool (leb a b) true`,
-- so lebRefl / lebTrans / lteAntisym / a leTotal from lebComplete fill the
-- slots directly; cmpEq / cmpLe come from the compareFromLe characterization
-- lemmas compareFromLeEq / compareFromLeLt, written GENERAL over any carrier so
-- Int and Frac reuse them). Int is constructor-case analysis: `ileb` compares
-- by sign quadrant (two nonnegs by leb, two negsuccs by leb with the operands
-- SWAPPED since negsucc k denotes -(k+1), mixed cases by constant), `ieqb` the
-- diagonal, and each Int law reduces its four cases to the matching Whole
-- lemma.
--
-- THE FRAC RESPECT PROOF, IN FULL: POSITIVE SCALING, NOT CANCELLATION. This is
-- the campaign's real content. Frac is the quotient of QPair under cross-
-- multiplication, and order does NOT lift for free the way the field
-- operations did. `leF x y` compares representatives by the cross term
-- `ileb (imul (qnum p) (qden q)) (imul (qnum q) (qden p))`, and to descend to
-- the quotient it must RESPECT the relation: changing a representative for a
-- cross-equal one must not change the verdict. The single fact that buys this
-- is ordered-semiring MONOTONICITY:
--
--   ilebMulPosR : ileb (imul a (nonneg (succ d))) (imul b (nonneg (succ d)))
--                   ==  ileb a b
--
-- scaling BOTH sides of an Int comparison by a POSITIVE Int (nonneg (succ d))
-- leaves the comparison unchanged. It both PRESERVES and REFLECTS the order, so
-- it is stated as a Bool equality of the two comparisons. It rests on the Whole
-- fact `lebMulPosR` (a clean two-level induction reducing "scale both sides by
-- d+1" to `lebAddSameL`, "add the same amount to both sides", plus the induction
-- hypothesis), lifted across the four sign quadrants; the only friction is that
-- `imul (negsucc _) (positive)` does not reduce definitionally (the succ head is
-- buried under a left-recursive mulW / addW), so `imulNegPos` supplies the one
-- dmulSucc rewrite that exposes the negsucc. THIS IS MONOTONICITY, categorically
-- NOT the forbidden multiplicative cancellation `imul k a = imul k b -> a = b`.
-- The campaign proves no cancellation and no gcd fact anywhere.
--
-- On ilebMulPosR the respect proofs `leRespL` / `leRespR` (one representative at
-- a time, mirroring the field-laws addRespL / addRespR) go through: to move the
-- right representative from q to q' under q ~ q', scale the cross term up by the
-- OTHER pair's positive denominator (ilebMulPosR), rewrite the numerators with
-- the QRel equation (a pure product swap, imulSwap3R, glued by congIleb2), and
-- scale back down. Unlike the field laws the middle rewrite lands in a Bool
-- comparison, not a QRel closed by qsound. leF then double-qlifts exactly as
-- addF does; `eqF x y` is `and (leF x y) (leF y x)`, quotient equality via
-- antisymmetry, reusing leF's respect proof with NO new obligation. (This is
-- the And built on BoolElim, `and`, not the case-based `andB`, so the ready
-- andTrueL / andTrueR / andBoth lemmas make decEqLawsFrac trivial; the two are
-- the same conjunction.) Of the six Frac order laws, transitivity scales each
-- hypothesis by the other's denominator and chains through the shared middle,
-- and antisymmetry is the CLEANEST: cross `<=` both ways forces the cross terms
-- EQUAL by ilebAntisymP, which is DEFINITIONALLY `QRel p q`, and qsound turns
-- that identification into `Eq Frac x y`. No cancellation, no gcd, no lowest
-- terms.
--
-- THIS CHAPTER'S SCOPE. It carries the ORDERING + DECEQ + ORD section of the
-- prelude IN FULL -- the Ordering type, the two ops classes and their two laws
-- records, the comparison defaults and their characterization, and the Whole /
-- Int / Frac instances with all six laws each -- prelude bodies mirrored
-- verbatim, together with the transitive closure of Whole / Bool / Int / Frac
-- supporting machinery the section needs (the difference-model Int ring
-- algebra, the leb order corpus, the quotient Frac ops), so the chapter loads
-- with NO prelude, exactly as the ch572 / ch573 pattern. Narration lives only
-- in these comments; every definition below is character-for-character its
-- prelude twin.


-- ============================================================
-- SUPPORTING CLOSURE, mirrored verbatim from the prelude. Bool, Whole,
-- and the Int difference-model ring algebra (ch572's method) plus the
-- quotient Frac ops (ch573's) are restated here so the chapter is self
-- contained. Nothing in this block is new; skip to THE ORD CLASSES for
-- the chapter's subject.
-- ============================================================
data Whole : U is
  zero : Whole
| succ : Whole -> Whole
end

builtin nat Whole zero succ

addW : Whole -> Whole -> Whole is
  fn (m : Whole) (n : Whole) is
    case m of
    | zero -> n
    | succ k with ih -> succ ih
    end
  end
end

-- Accelerate addition on closed literals: `4000 + 4000` takes one bigint step
-- instead of building a succ-chain. Registration runs a differential gate (the
-- unfolded body must equal bigint add on a battery of pairs), so this stays
-- kernel-sound; it fires ONLY when both arguments are NatLit.
builtin natAdd addW

mulW : Whole -> Whole -> Whole is
  fn (m : Whole) (n : Whole) is
    case m of
    | zero -> 0
    | succ k with ih -> addW ih n
    end
  end
end

-- Accelerate multiplication likewise - what makes `4000 * 4000` instant instead
-- of materialising 16 million succ nodes (and overflowing the stack at readback).
builtin natMul mulW

pred : Whole -> Whole is
  fn (n : Whole) is
    case n of
    | zero -> 0
    | succ k -> k
    end
  end
end

subW : Whole -> Whole -> Whole is
  fn (m : Whole) (n : Whole) is
    case n of
    | zero -> m
    | succ k with ih -> pred ih
    end
  end
end

-- Accelerate truncated subtraction (saturating monus) on closed literals.
builtin natMonus subW

data Bool : U is
  true : Bool
| false : Bool
end

leb : Whole -> Whole -> Bool is
  fn (m : Whole) is
    case m of
    | zero -> fn (n : Whole) is true end
    | succ k with ih -> fn (n : Whole) is
        case n of
        | zero -> false
        | succ j -> ih j
        end
      end
    end
  end
end

symEq : (A : U) -> (x : A) -> (y : A) -> Eq A x y -> Eq A y x is
  fn (A : U) (x : A) (y : A) (p : Eq A x y) is
    subst A x y p (fn (z : A) is Eq A z x end) (refl x)
  end
end

transEq : (A : U) -> (x : A) -> (y : A) -> (z : A) -> Eq A x y -> Eq A y z -> Eq A x z is
  fn (A : U) (x : A) (y : A) (z : A) (p : Eq A x y) (q : Eq A y z) is
    subst A y z q (fn (w : A) is Eq A x w end) p
  end
end

isZero : Whole -> Bool is
  fn (n : Whole) is case n of | zero -> true | succ k -> false end end
end

subWSucc : (a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Eq Whole (subW (succ a) (succ b)) (subW a b) is
  fn (a : Whole) (b : Whole) is
    WholeElim (fn (x : Whole) is Eq Whole (subW (succ a) (succ x)) (subW a x) end)
      (refl a)
      (fn (k : Whole) (ih : Eq Whole (subW (succ a) (succ k)) (subW a k)) is
         subst Whole (subW (succ a) (succ k)) (subW a k) ih
           (fn (z : Whole) is Eq Whole (subW (succ a) (succ (succ k))) (pred z) end)
           (refl (subW (succ a) (succ (succ k))))
       end)
      b
  end
end

isPos : Whole -> Bool is
  fn (n : Whole) is
    case n of
    | zero -> false
    | succ k -> true
    end
  end
end

Nat : U is
  Sig Whole (fn (n : Whole) is Eq Bool (isPos n) true end)
end

one : Nat is
  Pair Whole (fn (n : Whole) is Eq Bool (isPos n) true end) (succ zero) (refl true)
end

data Int : U is
  nonneg  : Whole -> Int
| negsucc : Whole -> Int
end

ineg : Int -> Int is
  fn (i : Int) is
    case i of
    | nonneg n -> case n of | zero -> nonneg zero | succ k -> negsucc k end
    | negsucc k -> nonneg (succ k)
    end
  end
end

wsub : Whole -> Whole -> Int is
  fn (a : Whole) (b : Whole) is
    case leb b a of
    | true -> nonneg (subW a b)
    | false -> negsucc (subW b (succ a))
    end
  end
end

imul : Int -> Int -> Int is
  fn (x : Int) (y : Int) is
    case x of
    | nonneg a ->
        case y of
        | nonneg c -> nonneg (mulW a c)
        | negsucc d -> ineg (nonneg (mulW a (succ d)))
        end
    | negsucc b ->
        case y of
        | nonneg c -> ineg (nonneg (mulW (succ b) c))
        | negsucc d -> nonneg (mulW (succ b) (succ d))
        end
    end
  end
end

And : U -> U -> U is fn (P : U) (Q : U) is Sig P (fn (_p : P) is Q end) end end

mkAnd : (P : U) -> (Q : U) -> P -> Q -> And P Q is
  fn (P : U) (Q : U) (p : P) (q : Q) is Pair P (fn (_p : P) is Q end) p q end
end

AssocT : (A : U) -> (A -> A -> A) -> U is
  fn (A : U) (f : A -> A -> A) is (a : A) -> (b : A) -> (c : A) -> Eq A (f (f a b) c) (f a (f b c)) end
end

CommT : (A : U) -> (A -> A -> A) -> U is
  fn (A : U) (f : A -> A -> A) is (a : A) -> (b : A) -> Eq A (f a b) (f b a) end
end

IdRT : (A : U) -> (A -> A -> A) -> A -> U is
  fn (A : U) (f : A -> A -> A) (e : A) is (a : A) -> Eq A (f a e) a end
end

DistribLT : (A : U) -> (A -> A -> A) -> (A -> A -> A) -> U is
  fn (A : U) (add : A -> A -> A) (mul : A -> A -> A) is
    (a : A) -> (b : A) -> (c : A) -> Eq A (mul a (add b c)) (add (mul a b) (mul a c))
  end
end

DistribRT : (A : U) -> (A -> A -> A) -> (A -> A -> A) -> U is
  fn (A : U) (add : A -> A -> A) (mul : A -> A -> A) is
    (a : A) -> (b : A) -> (c : A) -> Eq A (mul (add a b) c) (add (mul a c) (mul b c))
  end
end

AnnihRT : (A : U) -> (A -> A -> A) -> A -> U is
  fn (A : U) (mul : A -> A -> A) (z : A) is (a : A) -> Eq A (mul a z) z end
end

congW : (f : Whole -> Whole) -> (x : Whole) -> (y : Whole) -> Eq Whole x y -> Eq Whole (f x) (f y) is
  fn (f : Whole -> Whole) (x : Whole) (y : Whole) (p : Eq Whole x y) is
    subst Whole x y p (fn (z : Whole) is Eq Whole (f x) (f z) end) (refl (f x))
  end
end

addWAssoc : AssocT Whole addW is
  fn (a : Whole) (b : Whole) (c : Whole) is
    WholeElim (fn (x : Whole) is Eq Whole (addW (addW x b) c) (addW x (addW b c)) end)
      (refl (addW b c))
      (fn (k : Whole) (ih : Eq Whole (addW (addW k b) c) (addW k (addW b c))) is
         subst Whole (addW (addW k b) c) (addW k (addW b c)) ih
           (fn (z : Whole) is Eq Whole (succ (addW (addW k b) c)) (succ z) end)
           (refl (succ (addW (addW k b) c)))
       end)
      a
  end
end

addWZeroR : IdRT Whole addW zero is
  fn (a : Whole) is
    WholeElim (fn (x : Whole) is Eq Whole (addW x zero) x end)
      (refl zero)
      (fn (k : Whole) (ih : Eq Whole (addW k zero) k) is
         subst Whole (addW k zero) k ih
           (fn (z : Whole) is Eq Whole (addW (succ k) zero) (succ z) end)
           (refl (addW (succ k) zero))
       end)
      a
  end
end

addWSuccR : (m : Whole) -> (n : Whole) -> Eq Whole (addW m (succ n)) (succ (addW m n)) is
  fn (m : Whole) (n : Whole) is
    WholeElim (fn (x : Whole) is Eq Whole (addW x (succ n)) (succ (addW x n)) end)
      (refl (succ n))
      (fn (k : Whole) (ih : Eq Whole (addW k (succ n)) (succ (addW k n))) is
         subst Whole (addW k (succ n)) (succ (addW k n)) ih
           (fn (z : Whole) is Eq Whole (addW (succ k) (succ n)) (succ z) end)
           (refl (addW (succ k) (succ n)))
       end)
      m
  end
end

addWComm : CommT Whole addW is
  fn (a : Whole) (b : Whole) is
    WholeElim (fn (x : Whole) is Eq Whole (addW x b) (addW b x) end)
      (subst Whole (addW b zero) b (addWZeroR b)
         (fn (z : Whole) is Eq Whole z (addW b zero) end)
         (refl (addW b zero)))
      (fn (k : Whole) (ih : Eq Whole (addW k b) (addW b k)) is
         subst Whole (succ (addW b k)) (addW b (succ k))
           (subst Whole (addW b (succ k)) (succ (addW b k)) (addWSuccR b k)
              (fn (z : Whole) is Eq Whole z (addW b (succ k)) end)
              (refl (addW b (succ k))))
           (fn (z : Whole) is Eq Whole (succ (addW k b)) z end)
           (subst Whole (addW k b) (addW b k) ih
              (fn (z : Whole) is Eq Whole (succ (addW k b)) (succ z) end)
              (refl (succ (addW k b))))
       end)
      a
  end
end

addWSwapR : (x : Whole) -> (y : Whole) -> (w : Whole) -> Eq Whole (addW (addW x y) w) (addW (addW x w) y) is
  fn (x : Whole) (y : Whole) (w : Whole) is
    transEq Whole (addW (addW x y) w) (addW x (addW y w)) (addW (addW x w) y)
      (addWAssoc x y w)
      (transEq Whole (addW x (addW y w)) (addW x (addW w y)) (addW (addW x w) y)
         (congW (fn (t : Whole) is addW x t end) (addW y w) (addW w y) (addWComm y w))
         (symEq Whole (addW (addW x w) y) (addW x (addW w y)) (addWAssoc x w y)))
  end
end

addWShiftSucc : (a : Whole) -> (x : Whole) -> (y : Whole)
  -> Eq Whole (addW (addW a x) (succ y)) (addW (addW a y) (succ x)) is
  fn (a : Whole) (x : Whole) (y : Whole) is
    transEq Whole (addW (addW a x) (succ y)) (addW a (addW x (succ y))) (addW (addW a y) (succ x))
      (addWAssoc a x (succ y))
      (transEq Whole (addW a (addW x (succ y))) (addW a (succ (addW y x))) (addW (addW a y) (succ x))
         (congW (fn (t : Whole) is addW a t end) (addW x (succ y)) (succ (addW y x))
            (transEq Whole (addW x (succ y)) (succ (addW x y)) (succ (addW y x))
               (addWSuccR x y)
               (congW (fn (t : Whole) is succ t end) (addW x y) (addW y x) (addWComm x y))))
         (transEq Whole (addW a (succ (addW y x))) (addW a (addW y (succ x))) (addW (addW a y) (succ x))
            (congW (fn (t : Whole) is addW a t end) (succ (addW y x)) (addW y (succ x))
               (symEq Whole (addW y (succ x)) (succ (addW y x)) (addWSuccR y x)))
            (symEq Whole (addW (addW a y) (succ x)) (addW a (addW y (succ x))) (addWAssoc a y (succ x)))))
  end
end

mulWZeroR : AnnihRT Whole mulW zero is
  fn (a : Whole) is
    WholeElim (fn (x : Whole) is Eq Whole (mulW x zero) zero end)
      (refl zero)
      (fn (k : Whole) (ih : Eq Whole (mulW k zero) zero) is
         transEq Whole (mulW (succ k) zero) (mulW k zero) zero
           (addWZeroR (mulW k zero))
           ih
       end)
      a
  end
end

distribWR : DistribRT Whole addW mulW is
  fn (a : Whole) (b : Whole) (c : Whole) is
    WholeElim (fn (x : Whole) is Eq Whole (mulW (addW x b) c) (addW (mulW x c) (mulW b c)) end)
      (refl (mulW b c))
      (fn (k : Whole) (ih : Eq Whole (mulW (addW k b) c) (addW (mulW k c) (mulW b c))) is
         transEq Whole
           (addW (mulW (addW k b) c) c)
           (addW (addW (mulW k c) (mulW b c)) c)
           (addW (addW (mulW k c) c) (mulW b c))
           (congW (fn (t : Whole) is addW t c end) (mulW (addW k b) c) (addW (mulW k c) (mulW b c)) ih)
           (addWSwapR (mulW k c) (mulW b c) c)
       end)
      a
  end
end

mulWSuccR : (n : Whole) -> (m : Whole) -> Eq Whole (mulW n (succ m)) (addW (mulW n m) n) is
  fn (n : Whole) (m : Whole) is
    WholeElim (fn (x : Whole) is Eq Whole (mulW x (succ m)) (addW (mulW x m) x) end)
      (refl zero)
      (fn (k : Whole) (ih : Eq Whole (mulW k (succ m)) (addW (mulW k m) k)) is
         transEq Whole
           (addW (mulW k (succ m)) (succ m))
           (addW (addW (mulW k m) k) (succ m))
           (addW (addW (mulW k m) m) (succ k))
           (congW (fn (t : Whole) is addW t (succ m) end) (mulW k (succ m)) (addW (mulW k m) k) ih)
           (addWShiftSucc (mulW k m) k m)
       end)
      n
  end
end

mulWComm : CommT Whole mulW is
  fn (a : Whole) (b : Whole) is
    WholeElim (fn (x : Whole) is Eq Whole (mulW x b) (mulW b x) end)
      (subst Whole (mulW b zero) zero (mulWZeroR b)
         (fn (z : Whole) is Eq Whole z (mulW b zero) end)
         (refl (mulW b zero)))
      (fn (k : Whole) (ih : Eq Whole (mulW k b) (mulW b k)) is
         transEq Whole (mulW (succ k) b) (addW (mulW b k) b) (mulW b (succ k))
           (congW (fn (t : Whole) is addW t b end) (mulW k b) (mulW b k) ih)
           (symEq Whole (mulW b (succ k)) (addW (mulW b k) b) (mulWSuccR b k))
       end)
      a
  end
end

mulWAssoc : AssocT Whole mulW is
  fn (a : Whole) (b : Whole) (c : Whole) is
    WholeElim (fn (x : Whole) is Eq Whole (mulW (mulW x b) c) (mulW x (mulW b c)) end)
      (refl zero)
      (fn (k : Whole) (ih : Eq Whole (mulW (mulW k b) c) (mulW k (mulW b c))) is
         transEq Whole
           (mulW (mulW (succ k) b) c)
           (addW (mulW (mulW k b) c) (mulW b c))
           (mulW (succ k) (mulW b c))
           (distribWR (mulW k b) b c)
           (congW (fn (t : Whole) is addW t (mulW b c) end) (mulW (mulW k b) c) (mulW k (mulW b c)) ih)
       end)
      a
  end
end

distribWL : DistribLT Whole addW mulW is
  fn (a : Whole) (b : Whole) (c : Whole) is
    transEq Whole
      (mulW a (addW b c))
      (mulW (addW b c) a)
      (addW (mulW a b) (mulW a c))
      (mulWComm a (addW b c))
      (transEq Whole
         (mulW (addW b c) a)
         (addW (mulW b a) (mulW c a))
         (addW (mulW a b) (mulW a c))
         (distribWR b c a)
         (transEq Whole
            (addW (mulW b a) (mulW c a))
            (addW (mulW a b) (mulW c a))
            (addW (mulW a b) (mulW a c))
            (congW (fn (t : Whole) is addW t (mulW c a) end) (mulW b a) (mulW a b) (mulWComm b a))
            (congW (fn (t : Whole) is addW (mulW a b) t end) (mulW c a) (mulW a c) (mulWComm c a))))
  end
end

succInj : (a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Eq Whole (succ a) (succ b) -> Eq Whole a b is
  fn (a : Whole) (b : Whole) (p : Eq Whole (succ a) (succ b)) is
    congW pred (succ a) (succ b) p
  end
end

boolDiscTF : (G : U) -> Eq Bool true false -> G is
  fn (G : U) (h : Eq Bool true false) is
    subst Bool true false h
      (fn (z : Bool) is
         case z of
         | true -> Eq Bool true true
         | false -> G
         end
       end)
      (refl true)
  end
end

boolCaseEq : (g : Bool) -> (P : Bool -> U)
  -> (Eq Bool g true -> P true) -> (Eq Bool g false -> P false) -> P g is
  fn (g : Bool) (P : Bool -> U)
     (ht : Eq Bool g true -> P true) (hf : Eq Bool g false -> P false) is
    BoolElim (fn (x : Bool) is Eq Bool g x -> P x end) ht hf g (refl g)
  end
end

congNonneg : (x : Whole) -> (y : Whole) -> Eq Whole x y -> Eq Int (nonneg x) (nonneg y) is
  fn (x : Whole) (y : Whole) (p : Eq Whole x y) is
    subst Whole x y p (fn (z : Whole) is Eq Int (nonneg x) (nonneg z) end) (refl (nonneg x))
  end
end

congNegsucc : (x : Whole) -> (y : Whole) -> Eq Whole x y -> Eq Int (negsucc x) (negsucc y) is
  fn (x : Whole) (y : Whole) (p : Eq Whole x y) is
    subst Whole x y p (fn (z : Whole) is Eq Int (negsucc x) (negsucc z) end) (refl (negsucc x))
  end
end

lebComplete : (a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Eq Bool (leb a b) false -> Eq Bool (leb b a) true is
  fn (a : Whole) is
    WholeElim (fn (x : Whole) is (b : Whole) -> Eq Bool (leb x b) false -> Eq Bool (leb b x) true end)
      (fn (b : Whole) (h : Eq Bool (leb zero b) false) is
         boolDiscTF (Eq Bool (leb b zero) true) h end)
      (fn (k : Whole) (ih : (b : Whole) -> Eq Bool (leb k b) false -> Eq Bool (leb b k) true) is
         fn (b : Whole) is
           WholeElim (fn (y : Whole) is Eq Bool (leb (succ k) y) false -> Eq Bool (leb y (succ k)) true end)
             (fn (h : Eq Bool (leb (succ k) zero) false) is refl true end)
             (fn (j : Whole) (ihb : Eq Bool (leb (succ k) j) false -> Eq Bool (leb j (succ k)) true) is
                fn (h : Eq Bool (leb (succ k) (succ j)) false) is ih j h end end)
             b
         end end)
      a
  end
end

subWAddCancel : (a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Eq Bool (leb b a) true -> Eq Whole (addW b (subW a b)) a is
  fn (a : Whole) (b : Whole) is
    WholeElim (fn (x : Whole) is (m : Whole) -> Eq Bool (leb x m) true -> Eq Whole (addW x (subW m x)) m end)
      (fn (m : Whole) (h : Eq Bool (leb zero m) true) is refl m end)
      (fn (k : Whole) (ih : (m : Whole) -> Eq Bool (leb k m) true -> Eq Whole (addW k (subW m k)) m) is
         fn (m : Whole) is
           WholeElim (fn (y : Whole) is Eq Bool (leb (succ k) y) true -> Eq Whole (addW (succ k) (subW y (succ k))) y end)
             (fn (h : Eq Bool (leb (succ k) zero) true) is
                boolDiscTF (Eq Whole (addW (succ k) (subW zero (succ k))) zero)
                  (symEq Bool (leb (succ k) zero) true h) end)
             (fn (j : Whole) (ihb : Eq Bool (leb (succ k) j) true -> Eq Whole (addW (succ k) (subW j (succ k))) j) is
                fn (h : Eq Bool (leb (succ k) (succ j)) true) is
                  congW (fn (t : Whole) is succ t end) (addW k (subW (succ j) (succ k))) j
                    (transEq Whole (addW k (subW (succ j) (succ k))) (addW k (subW j k)) j
                       (congW (fn (t : Whole) is addW k t end) (subW (succ j) (succ k)) (subW j k) (subWSucc j k))
                       (ih j h))
                end end)
             m
         end end)
      b
      a
  end
end

addWCancelL : (k : Whole) -> (a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Eq Whole (addW k a) (addW k b) -> Eq Whole a b is
  fn (k : Whole) (a : Whole) (b : Whole) is
    WholeElim (fn (x : Whole) is Eq Whole (addW x a) (addW x b) -> Eq Whole a b end)
      (fn (h : Eq Whole (addW zero a) (addW zero b)) is h end)
      (fn (n : Whole) (ih : Eq Whole (addW n a) (addW n b) -> Eq Whole a b) is
         fn (h : Eq Whole (addW (succ n) a) (addW (succ n) b)) is
           ih (succInj (addW n a) (addW n b) h)
         end end)
      k
  end
end

lebSelfAddR : (m : Whole) -> (n : Whole) -> Eq Bool (leb m (addW m n)) true is
  fn (m : Whole) (n : Whole) is
    WholeElim (fn (x : Whole) is Eq Bool (leb x (addW x n)) true end)
      (refl true)
      (fn (k : Whole) (ih : Eq Bool (leb k (addW k n)) true) is ih end)
      m
  end
end

lebComplStrict : (a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Eq Bool (leb b a) false -> Eq Bool (leb (succ a) b) true is
  fn (a : Whole) (b : Whole) is
    WholeElim (fn (y : Whole) is (w : Whole) -> Eq Bool (leb y w) false -> Eq Bool (leb (succ w) y) true end)
      (fn (w : Whole) (h : Eq Bool (leb zero w) false) is
         boolDiscTF (Eq Bool (leb (succ w) zero) true) h end)
      (fn (j : Whole) (ih : (w : Whole) -> Eq Bool (leb j w) false -> Eq Bool (leb (succ w) j) true) is
         fn (w : Whole) is
           WholeElim (fn (x : Whole) is Eq Bool (leb (succ j) x) false -> Eq Bool (leb (succ x) (succ j)) true end)
             (fn (h : Eq Bool (leb (succ j) zero) false) is refl true end)
             (fn (i : Whole) (ihx : Eq Bool (leb (succ j) i) false -> Eq Bool (leb (succ i) (succ j)) true) is
                fn (h : Eq Bool (leb (succ j) (succ i)) false) is ih i h end end)
             w
         end end)
      b
      a
  end
end

orderTransfer : (a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> (c : Whole) -> (d : Whole)
  -> Eq Whole (addW a d) (addW c b) -> Eq Bool (leb b a) true -> Eq Bool (leb d c) true is
  fn (a : Whole) (b : Whole) (c : Whole) (d : Whole)
     (H : Eq Whole (addW a d) (addW c b)) (e1 : Eq Bool (leb b a) true) is
    let ba : Eq Whole (addW b (subW a b)) a = subWAddCancel a b e1 in
    let Hsub : Eq Whole (addW (addW b (subW a b)) d) (addW c b) =
      subst Whole a (addW b (subW a b)) (symEq Whole (addW b (subW a b)) a ba)
        (fn (z : Whole) is Eq Whole (addW z d) (addW c b) end) H in
    let step : Eq Whole (addW b (addW (subW a b) d)) (addW b c) =
      transEq Whole (addW b (addW (subW a b) d)) (addW (addW b (subW a b)) d) (addW b c)
        (symEq Whole (addW (addW b (subW a b)) d) (addW b (addW (subW a b) d)) (addWAssoc b (subW a b) d))
        (transEq Whole (addW (addW b (subW a b)) d) (addW c b) (addW b c) Hsub (addWComm c b)) in
    let rdc : Eq Whole (addW (subW a b) d) c = addWCancelL b (addW (subW a b) d) c step in
    let drc : Eq Whole (addW d (subW a b)) c =
      transEq Whole (addW d (subW a b)) (addW (subW a b) d) c (addWComm d (subW a b)) rdc in
    subst Whole (addW d (subW a b)) c drc (fn (z : Whole) is Eq Bool (leb d z) true end) (lebSelfAddR d (subW a b))
  end
end

subWCrossTrue : (a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> (c : Whole) -> (d : Whole)
  -> Eq Whole (addW a d) (addW c b)
  -> Eq Bool (leb b a) true -> Eq Bool (leb d c) true
  -> Eq Whole (subW a b) (subW c d) is
  fn (a : Whole) (b : Whole) (c : Whole) (d : Whole)
     (H : Eq Whole (addW a d) (addW c b))
     (e1 : Eq Bool (leb b a) true) (e2 : Eq Bool (leb d c) true) is
    let sac1 : Eq Whole (addW b (subW a b)) a = subWAddCancel a b e1 in
    let sac2 : Eq Whole (addW d (subW c d)) c = subWAddCancel c d e2 in
    let L1 : Eq Whole (addW (addW b d) (subW a b)) (addW a d) =
      transEq Whole (addW (addW b d) (subW a b)) (addW (addW b (subW a b)) d) (addW a d)
        (symEq Whole (addW (addW b (subW a b)) d) (addW (addW b d) (subW a b))
           (addWSwapR b (subW a b) d))
        (congW (fn (t : Whole) is addW t d end) (addW b (subW a b)) a sac1) in
    let R1 : Eq Whole (addW (addW b d) (subW c d)) (addW c b) =
      transEq Whole (addW (addW b d) (subW c d)) (addW (addW d b) (subW c d)) (addW c b)
        (congW (fn (t : Whole) is addW t (subW c d) end) (addW b d) (addW d b) (addWComm b d))
        (transEq Whole (addW (addW d b) (subW c d)) (addW (addW d (subW c d)) b) (addW c b)
           (symEq Whole (addW (addW d (subW c d)) b) (addW (addW d b) (subW c d))
              (addWSwapR d (subW c d) b))
           (congW (fn (t : Whole) is addW t b end) (addW d (subW c d)) c sac2)) in
    let E : Eq Whole (addW (addW b d) (subW a b)) (addW (addW b d) (subW c d)) =
      transEq Whole (addW (addW b d) (subW a b)) (addW a d) (addW (addW b d) (subW c d))
        L1
        (transEq Whole (addW a d) (addW c b) (addW (addW b d) (subW c d))
           H
           (symEq Whole (addW (addW b d) (subW c d)) (addW c b) R1)) in
    addWCancelL (addW b d) (subW a b) (subW c d) E
  end
end

subWCrossFalse : (a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> (c : Whole) -> (d : Whole)
  -> Eq Whole (addW a d) (addW c b)
  -> Eq Bool (leb b a) false -> Eq Bool (leb d c) false
  -> Eq Whole (subW b (succ a)) (subW d (succ c)) is
  fn (a : Whole) (b : Whole) (c : Whole) (d : Whole)
     (H : Eq Whole (addW a d) (addW c b))
     (e1 : Eq Bool (leb b a) false) (e2 : Eq Bool (leb d c) false) is
    let sac1 : Eq Whole (addW (succ a) (subW b (succ a))) b =
      subWAddCancel b (succ a) (lebComplStrict a b e1) in
    let sac2 : Eq Whole (addW (succ c) (subW d (succ c))) d =
      subWAddCancel d (succ c) (lebComplStrict c d e2) in
    let H1 : Eq Whole (addW a (addW (succ c) (subW d (succ c)))) (addW c b) =
      subst Whole d (addW (succ c) (subW d (succ c)))
        (symEq Whole (addW (succ c) (subW d (succ c))) d sac2)
        (fn (z : Whole) is Eq Whole (addW a z) (addW c b) end) H in
    let Hb : Eq Whole (addW a (addW (succ c) (subW d (succ c)))) (addW c (addW (succ a) (subW b (succ a)))) =
      subst Whole b (addW (succ a) (subW b (succ a)))
        (symEq Whole (addW (succ a) (subW b (succ a))) b sac1)
        (fn (z : Whole) is Eq Whole (addW a (addW (succ c) (subW d (succ c)))) (addW c z) end) H1 in
    let Llhs : Eq Whole (addW a (addW (succ c) (subW d (succ c)))) (succ (addW (addW a c) (subW d (succ c)))) =
      transEq Whole (addW a (addW (succ c) (subW d (succ c)))) (succ (addW a (addW c (subW d (succ c))))) (succ (addW (addW a c) (subW d (succ c))))
        (addWSuccR a (addW c (subW d (succ c))))
        (congW (fn (t : Whole) is succ t end) (addW a (addW c (subW d (succ c)))) (addW (addW a c) (subW d (succ c)))
           (symEq Whole (addW (addW a c) (subW d (succ c))) (addW a (addW c (subW d (succ c))))
              (addWAssoc a c (subW d (succ c))))) in
    let Rrhs : Eq Whole (addW c (addW (succ a) (subW b (succ a)))) (succ (addW (addW a c) (subW b (succ a)))) =
      transEq Whole (addW c (addW (succ a) (subW b (succ a)))) (succ (addW c (addW a (subW b (succ a))))) (succ (addW (addW a c) (subW b (succ a))))
        (addWSuccR c (addW a (subW b (succ a))))
        (congW (fn (t : Whole) is succ t end) (addW c (addW a (subW b (succ a)))) (addW (addW a c) (subW b (succ a)))
           (transEq Whole (addW c (addW a (subW b (succ a)))) (addW (addW c a) (subW b (succ a))) (addW (addW a c) (subW b (succ a)))
              (symEq Whole (addW (addW c a) (subW b (succ a))) (addW c (addW a (subW b (succ a))))
                 (addWAssoc c a (subW b (succ a))))
              (congW (fn (t : Whole) is addW t (subW b (succ a)) end) (addW c a) (addW a c) (addWComm c a)))) in
    let succEq : Eq Whole (succ (addW (addW a c) (subW d (succ c)))) (succ (addW (addW a c) (subW b (succ a)))) =
      transEq Whole (succ (addW (addW a c) (subW d (succ c)))) (addW a (addW (succ c) (subW d (succ c)))) (succ (addW (addW a c) (subW b (succ a))))
        (symEq Whole (addW a (addW (succ c) (subW d (succ c)))) (succ (addW (addW a c) (subW d (succ c)))) Llhs)
        (transEq Whole (addW a (addW (succ c) (subW d (succ c)))) (addW c (addW (succ a) (subW b (succ a)))) (succ (addW (addW a c) (subW b (succ a))))
           Hb Rrhs) in
    symEq Whole (subW d (succ c)) (subW b (succ a))
      (addWCancelL (addW a c) (subW d (succ c)) (subW b (succ a))
         (succInj (addW (addW a c) (subW d (succ c))) (addW (addW a c) (subW b (succ a))) succEq))
  end
end

wsubG : Bool -> Whole -> Whole -> Int is
  fn (g : Bool) (a : Whole) (b : Whole) is
    case g of
    | true -> nonneg (subW a b)
    | false -> negsucc (subW b (succ a))
    end
  end
end

wsubTrue : (a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Eq Bool (leb b a) true -> Eq Int (wsub a b) (nonneg (subW a b)) is
  fn (a : Whole) (b : Whole) (e : Eq Bool (leb b a) true) is
    subst Bool true (leb b a) (symEq Bool (leb b a) true e)
      (fn (g : Bool) is Eq Int (wsubG g a b) (nonneg (subW a b)) end)
      (refl (nonneg (subW a b)))
  end
end

wsubFalse : (a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Eq Bool (leb b a) false -> Eq Int (wsub a b) (negsucc (subW b (succ a))) is
  fn (a : Whole) (b : Whole) (e : Eq Bool (leb b a) false) is
    subst Bool false (leb b a) (symEq Bool (leb b a) false e)
      (fn (g : Bool) is Eq Int (wsubG g a b) (negsucc (subW b (succ a))) end)
      (refl (negsucc (subW b (succ a))))
  end
end

wsubEq : (a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> (c : Whole) -> (d : Whole)
  -> Eq Whole (addW a d) (addW c b) -> Eq Int (wsub a b) (wsub c d) is
  fn (a : Whole) (b : Whole) (c : Whole) (d : Whole) (H : Eq Whole (addW a d) (addW c b)) is
    boolCaseEq (leb b a)
      (fn (g1 : Bool) is Eq Int (wsub a b) (wsub c d) end)
      (fn (e1 : Eq Bool (leb b a) true) is
         boolCaseEq (leb d c)
           (fn (g2 : Bool) is Eq Int (wsub a b) (wsub c d) end)
           (fn (e2 : Eq Bool (leb d c) true) is
              transEq Int (wsub a b) (nonneg (subW a b)) (wsub c d)
                (wsubTrue a b e1)
                (transEq Int (nonneg (subW a b)) (nonneg (subW c d)) (wsub c d)
                   (congNonneg (subW a b) (subW c d) (subWCrossTrue a b c d H e1 e2))
                   (symEq Int (wsub c d) (nonneg (subW c d)) (wsubTrue c d e2)))
            end)
           (fn (e2 : Eq Bool (leb d c) false) is
              boolDiscTF (Eq Int (wsub a b) (wsub c d))
                (transEq Bool true (leb d c) false
                   (symEq Bool (leb d c) true (orderTransfer a b c d H e1)) e2)
            end)
       end)
      (fn (e1 : Eq Bool (leb b a) false) is
         boolCaseEq (leb d c)
           (fn (g2 : Bool) is Eq Int (wsub a b) (wsub c d) end)
           (fn (e2 : Eq Bool (leb d c) true) is
              boolDiscTF (Eq Int (wsub a b) (wsub c d))
                (transEq Bool true (leb b a) false
                   (symEq Bool (leb b a) true
                      (orderTransfer c d a b (symEq Whole (addW a d) (addW c b) H) e2))
                   e1)
            end)
           (fn (e2 : Eq Bool (leb d c) false) is
              transEq Int (wsub a b) (negsucc (subW b (succ a))) (wsub c d)
                (wsubFalse a b e1)
                (transEq Int (negsucc (subW b (succ a))) (negsucc (subW d (succ c))) (wsub c d)
                   (congNegsucc (subW b (succ a)) (subW d (succ c)) (subWCrossFalse a b c d H e1 e2))
                   (symEq Int (wsub c d) (negsucc (subW d (succ c))) (wsubFalse c d e2)))
            end)
       end)
  end
end

posP : Int -> Whole is
  fn (x : Int) is case x of | nonneg n -> n | negsucc k -> zero end end
end

negP : Int -> Whole is
  fn (x : Int) is case x of | nonneg n -> zero | negsucc k -> succ k end end
end

congWsub2 : (x1 : Whole) -> (y1 : Whole) -> (x2 : Whole) -> (y2 : Whole)
  -> Eq Whole x1 y1 -> Eq Whole x2 y2 -> Eq Int (wsub x1 x2) (wsub y1 y2) is
  fn (x1 : Whole) (y1 : Whole) (x2 : Whole) (y2 : Whole)
     (p1 : Eq Whole x1 y1) (p2 : Eq Whole x2 y2) is
    subst Whole x1 y1 p1 (fn (z : Whole) is Eq Int (wsub x1 x2) (wsub z y2) end)
      (subst Whole x2 y2 p2 (fn (w : Whole) is Eq Int (wsub x1 x2) (wsub x1 w) end)
         (refl (wsub x1 x2)))
  end
end

addWInterchange : (x : Whole) -> (y : Whole) -> (u : Whole) -> (v : Whole)
  -> Eq Whole (addW (addW x y) (addW u v)) (addW (addW x u) (addW y v)) is
  fn (x : Whole) (y : Whole) (u : Whole) (v : Whole) is
    transEq Whole (addW (addW x y) (addW u v)) (addW x (addW y (addW u v))) (addW (addW x u) (addW y v))
      (addWAssoc x y (addW u v))
      (transEq Whole (addW x (addW y (addW u v))) (addW x (addW u (addW y v))) (addW (addW x u) (addW y v))
         (congW (fn (s : Whole) is addW x s end) (addW y (addW u v)) (addW u (addW y v))
            (transEq Whole (addW y (addW u v)) (addW (addW y u) v) (addW u (addW y v))
               (symEq Whole (addW (addW y u) v) (addW y (addW u v)) (addWAssoc y u v))
               (transEq Whole (addW (addW y u) v) (addW (addW u y) v) (addW u (addW y v))
                  (congW (fn (s : Whole) is addW s v end) (addW y u) (addW u y) (addWComm y u))
                  (addWAssoc u y v))))
         (symEq Whole (addW (addW x u) (addW y v)) (addW x (addW u (addW y v))) (addWAssoc x u (addW y v))))
  end
end

inegNonneg : (m : Whole) -> Eq Int (ineg (nonneg m)) (wsub zero m) is
  fn (m : Whole) is
    WholeElim (fn (w : Whole) is Eq Int (ineg (nonneg w)) (wsub zero w) end)
      (refl (nonneg zero))
      (fn (k : Whole) (ih : Eq Int (ineg (nonneg k)) (wsub zero k)) is refl (negsucc k) end)
      m
  end
end

wsubPosNeg : (p : Whole) -> (n : Whole)
  -> Eq Whole (addW (posP (wsub p n)) n) (addW p (negP (wsub p n))) is
  fn (p : Whole) (n : Whole) is
    boolCaseEq (leb n p)
      (fn (g : Bool) is Eq Whole (addW (posP (wsub p n)) n) (addW p (negP (wsub p n))) end)
      (fn (e1 : Eq Bool (leb n p) true) is
         subst Int (nonneg (subW p n)) (wsub p n)
           (symEq Int (wsub p n) (nonneg (subW p n)) (wsubTrue p n e1))
           (fn (w : Int) is Eq Whole (addW (posP w) n) (addW p (negP w)) end)
           (transEq Whole (addW (subW p n) n) (addW n (subW p n)) (addW p zero)
              (addWComm (subW p n) n)
              (transEq Whole (addW n (subW p n)) p (addW p zero)
                 (subWAddCancel p n e1)
                 (symEq Whole (addW p zero) p (addWZeroR p))))
       end)
      (fn (e2 : Eq Bool (leb n p) false) is
         subst Int (negsucc (subW n (succ p))) (wsub p n)
           (symEq Int (wsub p n) (negsucc (subW n (succ p))) (wsubFalse p n e2))
           (fn (w : Int) is Eq Whole (addW (posP w) n) (addW p (negP w)) end)
           (transEq Whole n (succ (addW p (subW n (succ p)))) (addW p (succ (subW n (succ p))))
              (symEq Whole (succ (addW p (subW n (succ p)))) n
                 (subWAddCancel n (succ p) (lebComplStrict p n e2)))
              (symEq Whole (addW p (succ (subW n (succ p)))) (succ (addW p (subW n (succ p))))
                 (addWSuccR p (subW n (succ p)))))
       end)
  end
end

imulSpec : (x : Int) -> (y : Int)
  -> Eq Int (imul x y)
       (wsub (addW (mulW (posP x) (posP y)) (mulW (negP x) (negP y)))
             (addW (mulW (posP x) (negP y)) (mulW (negP x) (posP y)))) is
  fn (x : Int) (y : Int) is
    IntElim (fn (wx : Int) is Eq Int (imul wx y)
              (wsub (addW (mulW (posP wx) (posP y)) (mulW (negP wx) (negP y)))
                    (addW (mulW (posP wx) (negP y)) (mulW (negP wx) (posP y)))) end)
      (fn (a : Whole) is
         IntElim (fn (wy : Int) is Eq Int (imul (nonneg a) wy)
                   (wsub (addW (mulW (posP (nonneg a)) (posP wy)) (mulW (negP (nonneg a)) (negP wy)))
                         (addW (mulW (posP (nonneg a)) (negP wy)) (mulW (negP (nonneg a)) (posP wy)))) end)
           (fn (c : Whole) is
              congWsub2 (mulW a c) (addW (mulW a c) zero) zero (addW (mulW a zero) zero)
                (symEq Whole (addW (mulW a c) zero) (mulW a c) (addWZeroR (mulW a c)))
                (symEq Whole (addW (mulW a zero) zero) zero
                   (transEq Whole (addW (mulW a zero) zero) (mulW a zero) zero
                      (addWZeroR (mulW a zero)) (mulWZeroR a)))
            end)
           (fn (d : Whole) is
              transEq Int (ineg (nonneg (mulW a (succ d)))) (wsub zero (mulW a (succ d)))
                (wsub (addW (mulW a zero) zero) (addW (mulW a (succ d)) zero))
                (inegNonneg (mulW a (succ d)))
                (congWsub2 zero (addW (mulW a zero) zero) (mulW a (succ d)) (addW (mulW a (succ d)) zero)
                   (symEq Whole (addW (mulW a zero) zero) zero
                      (transEq Whole (addW (mulW a zero) zero) (mulW a zero) zero
                         (addWZeroR (mulW a zero)) (mulWZeroR a)))
                   (symEq Whole (addW (mulW a (succ d)) zero) (mulW a (succ d)) (addWZeroR (mulW a (succ d)))))
            end)
           y
       end)
      (fn (b : Whole) is
         IntElim (fn (wy : Int) is Eq Int (imul (negsucc b) wy)
                   (wsub (addW (mulW (posP (negsucc b)) (posP wy)) (mulW (negP (negsucc b)) (negP wy)))
                         (addW (mulW (posP (negsucc b)) (negP wy)) (mulW (negP (negsucc b)) (posP wy)))) end)
           (fn (c : Whole) is
              transEq Int (ineg (nonneg (mulW (succ b) c))) (wsub zero (mulW (succ b) c))
                (wsub (mulW (succ b) zero) (mulW (succ b) c))
                (inegNonneg (mulW (succ b) c))
                (congWsub2 zero (mulW (succ b) zero) (mulW (succ b) c) (mulW (succ b) c)
                   (symEq Whole (mulW (succ b) zero) zero (mulWZeroR (succ b)))
                   (refl (mulW (succ b) c)))
            end)
           (fn (d : Whole) is
              congWsub2 (mulW (succ b) (succ d)) (mulW (succ b) (succ d)) zero (mulW (succ b) zero)
                (refl (mulW (succ b) (succ d)))
                (symEq Whole (mulW (succ b) zero) zero (mulWZeroR (succ b)))
            end)
           y
       end)
      x
  end
end

mulCrossIdent : (u : Whole) -> (v : Whole) -> (r : Whole) -> (w : Whole) -> (s : Whole) -> (t : Whole)
  -> Eq Whole (addW u w) (addW r v)
  -> Eq Whole (addW (addW (mulW u s) (mulW v t)) (addW (mulW r t) (mulW w s)))
              (addW (addW (mulW r s) (mulW w t)) (addW (mulW u t) (mulW v s))) is
  fn (u : Whole) (v : Whole) (r : Whole) (w : Whole) (s : Whole) (t : Whole)
     (hyp : Eq Whole (addW u w) (addW r v)) is
    let a1 : Whole = mulW u s in
    let a2 : Whole = mulW v t in
    let a3 : Whole = mulW r t in
    let a4 : Whole = mulW w s in
    let b1 : Whole = mulW r s in
    let b2 : Whole = mulW w t in
    let b3 : Whole = mulW u t in
    let b4 : Whole = mulW v s in
    let colPz : Eq Whole (addW a1 a4) (addW b1 b4)
      = transEq Whole (addW a1 a4) (mulW (addW u w) s) (addW b1 b4)
          (symEq Whole (mulW (addW u w) s) (addW a1 a4) (distribWR u w s))
          (transEq Whole (mulW (addW u w) s) (mulW (addW r v) s) (addW b1 b4)
             (congW (fn (zz : Whole) is mulW zz s end) (addW u w) (addW r v) hyp)
             (distribWR r v s)) in
    let vrEq : Eq Whole (addW v r) (addW w u)
      = transEq Whole (addW v r) (addW r v) (addW w u)
          (addWComm v r)
          (transEq Whole (addW r v) (addW u w) (addW w u)
             (symEq Whole (addW u w) (addW r v) hyp)
             (addWComm u w)) in
    let g2 : Eq Whole (addW a2 a3) (addW b2 b3)
      = transEq Whole (addW a2 a3) (mulW (addW v r) t) (addW b2 b3)
          (symEq Whole (mulW (addW v r) t) (addW a2 a3) (distribWR v r t))
          (transEq Whole (mulW (addW v r) t) (mulW (addW w u) t) (addW b2 b3)
             (congW (fn (zz : Whole) is mulW zz t end) (addW v r) (addW w u) vrEq)
             (distribWR w u t)) in
    let part1 : Eq Whole (addW (addW a1 a2) (addW a3 a4)) (addW (addW a1 a4) (addW a2 a3))
      = transEq Whole (addW (addW a1 a2) (addW a3 a4)) (addW (addW a1 a2) (addW a4 a3)) (addW (addW a1 a4) (addW a2 a3))
          (congW (fn (zz : Whole) is addW (addW a1 a2) zz end) (addW a3 a4) (addW a4 a3) (addWComm a3 a4))
          (addWInterchange a1 a2 a4 a3) in
    let part2 : Eq Whole (addW (addW a1 a4) (addW a2 a3)) (addW (addW b1 b4) (addW b2 b3))
      = transEq Whole (addW (addW a1 a4) (addW a2 a3)) (addW (addW b1 b4) (addW a2 a3)) (addW (addW b1 b4) (addW b2 b3))
          (congW (fn (zz : Whole) is addW zz (addW a2 a3) end) (addW a1 a4) (addW b1 b4) colPz)
          (congW (fn (zz : Whole) is addW (addW b1 b4) zz end) (addW a2 a3) (addW b2 b3) g2) in
    let part3 : Eq Whole (addW (addW b1 b4) (addW b2 b3)) (addW (addW b1 b2) (addW b3 b4))
      = transEq Whole (addW (addW b1 b4) (addW b2 b3)) (addW (addW b1 b2) (addW b4 b3)) (addW (addW b1 b2) (addW b3 b4))
          (addWInterchange b1 b4 b2 b3)
          (congW (fn (zz : Whole) is addW (addW b1 b2) zz end) (addW b4 b3) (addW b3 b4) (addWComm b4 b3)) in
    transEq Whole (addW (addW a1 a2) (addW a3 a4)) (addW (addW a1 a4) (addW a2 a3)) (addW (addW b1 b2) (addW b3 b4))
      part1
      (transEq Whole (addW (addW a1 a4) (addW a2 a3)) (addW (addW b1 b4) (addW b2 b3)) (addW (addW b1 b2) (addW b3 b4))
         part2 part3)
  end
end

imulWsub : (p : Whole) -> (n : Whole) -> (z : Int)
  -> Eq Int (imul (wsub p n) z)
       (wsub (addW (mulW p (posP z)) (mulW n (negP z)))
             (addW (mulW p (negP z)) (mulW n (posP z)))) is
  fn (p : Whole) (n : Whole) (z : Int) is
    let P0 : Whole = posP (wsub p n) in
    let N0 : Whole = negP (wsub p n) in
    let pz : Whole = posP z in
    let nz : Whole = negP z in
    let K : Eq Whole (addW P0 n) (addW p N0) = wsubPosNeg p n in
    let H : Eq Whole (addW (addW (mulW P0 pz) (mulW N0 nz)) (addW (mulW p nz) (mulW n pz)))
                     (addW (addW (mulW p pz) (mulW n nz)) (addW (mulW P0 nz) (mulW N0 pz)))
      = mulCrossIdent P0 N0 p n pz nz K in
    transEq Int (imul (wsub p n) z)
      (wsub (addW (mulW P0 pz) (mulW N0 nz)) (addW (mulW P0 nz) (mulW N0 pz)))
      (wsub (addW (mulW p pz) (mulW n nz)) (addW (mulW p nz) (mulW n pz)))
      (imulSpec (wsub p n) z)
      (wsubEq (addW (mulW P0 pz) (mulW N0 nz)) (addW (mulW P0 nz) (mulW N0 pz))
              (addW (mulW p pz) (mulW n nz)) (addW (mulW p nz) (mulW n pz)) H)
  end
end

cong2W : (f : Whole -> Whole -> Whole) -> (x1 : Whole) -> (y1 : Whole) -> (x2 : Whole) -> (y2 : Whole)
  -> Eq Whole x1 y1 -> Eq Whole x2 y2 -> Eq Whole (f x1 x2) (f y1 y2) is
  fn (f : Whole -> Whole -> Whole) (x1 : Whole) (y1 : Whole) (x2 : Whole) (y2 : Whole)
     (p1 : Eq Whole x1 y1) (p2 : Eq Whole x2 y2) is
    transEq Whole (f x1 x2) (f y1 x2) (f y1 y2)
      (congW (fn (t : Whole) is f t x2 end) x1 y1 p1)
      (congW (fn (t : Whole) is f y1 t end) x2 y2 p2)
  end
end

congImulL : (x : Int) -> (x' : Int) -> (y : Int) -> Eq Int x x' -> Eq Int (imul x y) (imul x' y) is
  fn (x : Int) (x' : Int) (y : Int) (p : Eq Int x x') is
    subst Int x x' p (fn (z : Int) is Eq Int (imul x y) (imul z y) end) (refl (imul x y))
  end
end

congImulR : (x : Int) -> (y : Int) -> (y' : Int) -> Eq Int y y' -> Eq Int (imul x y) (imul x y') is
  fn (x : Int) (y : Int) (y' : Int) (p : Eq Int y y') is
    subst Int y y' p (fn (z : Int) is Eq Int (imul x y) (imul x z) end) (refl (imul x y))
  end
end

mulAssocCol : (a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> (c : Whole) -> (d : Whole) -> (e : Whole) -> (f : Whole)
  -> Eq Whole
       (addW (mulW (addW (mulW a c) (mulW b d)) e) (mulW (addW (mulW a d) (mulW b c)) f))
       (addW (mulW (addW (mulW c e) (mulW d f)) a) (mulW (addW (mulW c f) (mulW d e)) b)) is
  fn (a : Whole) (b : Whole) (c : Whole) (d : Whole) (e : Whole) (f : Whole) is
    let ace : Whole = mulW a (mulW c e) in
    let bde : Whole = mulW b (mulW d e) in
    let adf : Whole = mulW a (mulW d f) in
    let bcf : Whole = mulW b (mulW c f) in
    let canon : Whole = addW (mulW a (addW (mulW c e) (mulW d f))) (mulW b (addW (mulW c f) (mulW d e))) in
    let lhs2canon : Eq Whole
          (addW (mulW (addW (mulW a c) (mulW b d)) e) (mulW (addW (mulW a d) (mulW b c)) f))
          canon
      = transEq Whole
          (addW (mulW (addW (mulW a c) (mulW b d)) e) (mulW (addW (mulW a d) (mulW b c)) f))
          (addW (addW (mulW (mulW a c) e) (mulW (mulW b d) e)) (addW (mulW (mulW a d) f) (mulW (mulW b c) f)))
          canon
          (cong2W (fn (u : Whole) (v : Whole) is addW u v end)
             (mulW (addW (mulW a c) (mulW b d)) e) (addW (mulW (mulW a c) e) (mulW (mulW b d) e))
             (mulW (addW (mulW a d) (mulW b c)) f) (addW (mulW (mulW a d) f) (mulW (mulW b c) f))
             (distribWR (mulW a c) (mulW b d) e)
             (distribWR (mulW a d) (mulW b c) f))
          (transEq Whole
             (addW (addW (mulW (mulW a c) e) (mulW (mulW b d) e)) (addW (mulW (mulW a d) f) (mulW (mulW b c) f)))
             (addW (addW ace bde) (addW adf bcf))
             canon
             (cong2W (fn (u : Whole) (v : Whole) is addW u v end)
                (addW (mulW (mulW a c) e) (mulW (mulW b d) e)) (addW ace bde)
                (addW (mulW (mulW a d) f) (mulW (mulW b c) f)) (addW adf bcf)
                (cong2W (fn (u : Whole) (v : Whole) is addW u v end)
                   (mulW (mulW a c) e) ace (mulW (mulW b d) e) bde
                   (mulWAssoc a c e) (mulWAssoc b d e))
                (cong2W (fn (u : Whole) (v : Whole) is addW u v end)
                   (mulW (mulW a d) f) adf (mulW (mulW b c) f) bcf
                   (mulWAssoc a d f) (mulWAssoc b c f)))
             (transEq Whole
                (addW (addW ace bde) (addW adf bcf))
                (addW (addW ace adf) (addW bde bcf))
                canon
                (addWInterchange ace bde adf bcf)
                (transEq Whole
                   (addW (addW ace adf) (addW bde bcf))
                   (addW (mulW a (addW (mulW c e) (mulW d f))) (mulW b (addW (mulW d e) (mulW c f))))
                   canon
                   (cong2W (fn (u : Whole) (v : Whole) is addW u v end)
                      (addW ace adf) (mulW a (addW (mulW c e) (mulW d f)))
                      (addW bde bcf) (mulW b (addW (mulW d e) (mulW c f)))
                      (symEq Whole (mulW a (addW (mulW c e) (mulW d f))) (addW ace adf) (distribWL a (mulW c e) (mulW d f)))
                      (symEq Whole (mulW b (addW (mulW d e) (mulW c f))) (addW bde bcf) (distribWL b (mulW d e) (mulW c f))))
                   (congW (fn (s : Whole) is addW (mulW a (addW (mulW c e) (mulW d f))) (mulW b s) end)
                      (addW (mulW d e) (mulW c f)) (addW (mulW c f) (mulW d e))
                      (addWComm (mulW d e) (mulW c f)))))) in
    transEq Whole
      (addW (mulW (addW (mulW a c) (mulW b d)) e) (mulW (addW (mulW a d) (mulW b c)) f))
      canon
      (addW (mulW (addW (mulW c e) (mulW d f)) a) (mulW (addW (mulW c f) (mulW d e)) b))
      lhs2canon
      (cong2W (fn (u : Whole) (v : Whole) is addW u v end)
         (mulW a (addW (mulW c e) (mulW d f))) (mulW (addW (mulW c e) (mulW d f)) a)
         (mulW b (addW (mulW c f) (mulW d e))) (mulW (addW (mulW c f) (mulW d e)) b)
         (mulWComm a (addW (mulW c e) (mulW d f)))
         (mulWComm b (addW (mulW c f) (mulW d e))))
  end
end

imulComm : CommT Int imul is
  fn (a : Int) (b : Int) is
    transEq Int (imul a b)
      (wsub (addW (mulW (posP a) (posP b)) (mulW (negP a) (negP b))) (addW (mulW (posP a) (negP b)) (mulW (negP a) (posP b))))
      (imul b a)
      (imulSpec a b)
      (transEq Int
         (wsub (addW (mulW (posP a) (posP b)) (mulW (negP a) (negP b))) (addW (mulW (posP a) (negP b)) (mulW (negP a) (posP b))))
         (wsub (addW (mulW (posP b) (posP a)) (mulW (negP b) (negP a))) (addW (mulW (posP b) (negP a)) (mulW (negP b) (posP a))))
         (imul b a)
         (congWsub2
            (addW (mulW (posP a) (posP b)) (mulW (negP a) (negP b))) (addW (mulW (posP b) (posP a)) (mulW (negP b) (negP a)))
            (addW (mulW (posP a) (negP b)) (mulW (negP a) (posP b))) (addW (mulW (posP b) (negP a)) (mulW (negP b) (posP a)))
            (cong2W (fn (u : Whole) (v : Whole) is addW u v end)
               (mulW (posP a) (posP b)) (mulW (posP b) (posP a)) (mulW (negP a) (negP b)) (mulW (negP b) (negP a))
               (mulWComm (posP a) (posP b)) (mulWComm (negP a) (negP b)))
            (transEq Whole
               (addW (mulW (posP a) (negP b)) (mulW (negP a) (posP b)))
               (addW (mulW (negP a) (posP b)) (mulW (posP a) (negP b)))
               (addW (mulW (posP b) (negP a)) (mulW (negP b) (posP a)))
               (addWComm (mulW (posP a) (negP b)) (mulW (negP a) (posP b)))
               (cong2W (fn (u : Whole) (v : Whole) is addW u v end)
                  (mulW (negP a) (posP b)) (mulW (posP b) (negP a)) (mulW (posP a) (negP b)) (mulW (negP b) (posP a))
                  (mulWComm (negP a) (posP b)) (mulWComm (posP a) (negP b)))))
         (symEq Int (imul b a)
            (wsub (addW (mulW (posP b) (posP a)) (mulW (negP b) (negP a))) (addW (mulW (posP b) (negP a)) (mulW (negP b) (posP a))))
            (imulSpec b a)))
  end
end

imulWsubR : (z : Int) -> (p : Whole) -> (n : Whole)
  -> Eq Int (imul z (wsub p n))
       (wsub (addW (mulW p (posP z)) (mulW n (negP z))) (addW (mulW p (negP z)) (mulW n (posP z)))) is
  fn (z : Int) (p : Whole) (n : Whole) is
    transEq Int (imul z (wsub p n)) (imul (wsub p n) z)
      (wsub (addW (mulW p (posP z)) (mulW n (negP z))) (addW (mulW p (negP z)) (mulW n (posP z))))
      (imulComm z (wsub p n))
      (imulWsub p n z)
  end
end

imulAssoc : AssocT Int imul is
  fn (a : Int) (b : Int) (c : Int) is
    transEq Int (imul (imul a b) c)
      (wsub (addW (mulW (addW (mulW (posP a) (posP b)) (mulW (negP a) (negP b))) (posP c)) (mulW (addW (mulW (posP a) (negP b)) (mulW (negP a) (posP b))) (negP c)))
            (addW (mulW (addW (mulW (posP a) (posP b)) (mulW (negP a) (negP b))) (negP c)) (mulW (addW (mulW (posP a) (negP b)) (mulW (negP a) (posP b))) (posP c))))
      (imul a (imul b c))
      (transEq Int (imul (imul a b) c)
         (imul (wsub (addW (mulW (posP a) (posP b)) (mulW (negP a) (negP b))) (addW (mulW (posP a) (negP b)) (mulW (negP a) (posP b)))) c)
         (wsub (addW (mulW (addW (mulW (posP a) (posP b)) (mulW (negP a) (negP b))) (posP c)) (mulW (addW (mulW (posP a) (negP b)) (mulW (negP a) (posP b))) (negP c)))
               (addW (mulW (addW (mulW (posP a) (posP b)) (mulW (negP a) (negP b))) (negP c)) (mulW (addW (mulW (posP a) (negP b)) (mulW (negP a) (posP b))) (posP c))))
         (congImulL (imul a b) (wsub (addW (mulW (posP a) (posP b)) (mulW (negP a) (negP b))) (addW (mulW (posP a) (negP b)) (mulW (negP a) (posP b)))) c (imulSpec a b))
         (imulWsub (addW (mulW (posP a) (posP b)) (mulW (negP a) (negP b))) (addW (mulW (posP a) (negP b)) (mulW (negP a) (posP b))) c))
      (transEq Int
         (wsub (addW (mulW (addW (mulW (posP a) (posP b)) (mulW (negP a) (negP b))) (posP c)) (mulW (addW (mulW (posP a) (negP b)) (mulW (negP a) (posP b))) (negP c)))
               (addW (mulW (addW (mulW (posP a) (posP b)) (mulW (negP a) (negP b))) (negP c)) (mulW (addW (mulW (posP a) (negP b)) (mulW (negP a) (posP b))) (posP c))))
         (wsub (addW (mulW (addW (mulW (posP b) (posP c)) (mulW (negP b) (negP c))) (posP a)) (mulW (addW (mulW (posP b) (negP c)) (mulW (negP b) (posP c))) (negP a)))
               (addW (mulW (addW (mulW (posP b) (posP c)) (mulW (negP b) (negP c))) (negP a)) (mulW (addW (mulW (posP b) (negP c)) (mulW (negP b) (posP c))) (posP a))))
         (imul a (imul b c))
         (congWsub2
            (addW (mulW (addW (mulW (posP a) (posP b)) (mulW (negP a) (negP b))) (posP c)) (mulW (addW (mulW (posP a) (negP b)) (mulW (negP a) (posP b))) (negP c)))
            (addW (mulW (addW (mulW (posP b) (posP c)) (mulW (negP b) (negP c))) (posP a)) (mulW (addW (mulW (posP b) (negP c)) (mulW (negP b) (posP c))) (negP a)))
            (addW (mulW (addW (mulW (posP a) (posP b)) (mulW (negP a) (negP b))) (negP c)) (mulW (addW (mulW (posP a) (negP b)) (mulW (negP a) (posP b))) (posP c)))
            (addW (mulW (addW (mulW (posP b) (posP c)) (mulW (negP b) (negP c))) (negP a)) (mulW (addW (mulW (posP b) (negP c)) (mulW (negP b) (posP c))) (posP a)))
            (mulAssocCol (posP a) (negP a) (posP b) (negP b) (posP c) (negP c))
            (transEq Whole
               (addW (mulW (addW (mulW (posP a) (posP b)) (mulW (negP a) (negP b))) (negP c)) (mulW (addW (mulW (posP a) (negP b)) (mulW (negP a) (posP b))) (posP c)))
               (addW (mulW (addW (mulW (posP b) (negP c)) (mulW (negP b) (posP c))) (posP a)) (mulW (addW (mulW (posP b) (posP c)) (mulW (negP b) (negP c))) (negP a)))
               (addW (mulW (addW (mulW (posP b) (posP c)) (mulW (negP b) (negP c))) (negP a)) (mulW (addW (mulW (posP b) (negP c)) (mulW (negP b) (posP c))) (posP a)))
               (mulAssocCol (posP a) (negP a) (posP b) (negP b) (negP c) (posP c))
               (addWComm (mulW (addW (mulW (posP b) (negP c)) (mulW (negP b) (posP c))) (posP a)) (mulW (addW (mulW (posP b) (posP c)) (mulW (negP b) (negP c))) (negP a)))))
         (symEq Int (imul a (imul b c))
            (wsub (addW (mulW (addW (mulW (posP b) (posP c)) (mulW (negP b) (negP c))) (posP a)) (mulW (addW (mulW (posP b) (negP c)) (mulW (negP b) (posP c))) (negP a)))
                  (addW (mulW (addW (mulW (posP b) (posP c)) (mulW (negP b) (negP c))) (negP a)) (mulW (addW (mulW (posP b) (negP c)) (mulW (negP b) (posP c))) (posP a))))
            (transEq Int (imul a (imul b c))
               (imul a (wsub (addW (mulW (posP b) (posP c)) (mulW (negP b) (negP c))) (addW (mulW (posP b) (negP c)) (mulW (negP b) (posP c)))))
               (wsub (addW (mulW (addW (mulW (posP b) (posP c)) (mulW (negP b) (negP c))) (posP a)) (mulW (addW (mulW (posP b) (negP c)) (mulW (negP b) (posP c))) (negP a)))
                     (addW (mulW (addW (mulW (posP b) (posP c)) (mulW (negP b) (negP c))) (negP a)) (mulW (addW (mulW (posP b) (negP c)) (mulW (negP b) (posP c))) (posP a))))
               (congImulR a (imul b c) (wsub (addW (mulW (posP b) (posP c)) (mulW (negP b) (negP c))) (addW (mulW (posP b) (negP c)) (mulW (negP b) (posP c)))) (imulSpec b c))
               (imulWsubR a (addW (mulW (posP b) (posP c)) (mulW (negP b) (negP c))) (addW (mulW (posP b) (negP c)) (mulW (negP b) (posP c)))))))
  end
end

data QPair : U is qpair : Int -> Whole -> QPair end

qnum   : QPair -> Int   is fn (p : QPair) is case p of | qpair i d -> i end end end

qdpred : QPair -> Whole is fn (p : QPair) is case p of | qpair i d -> d end end end

qden : QPair -> Int is fn (p : QPair) is nonneg (succ (qdpred p)) end end

QRel : QPair -> QPair -> Prop is
  fn (p : QPair) (q : QPair) is
    Eq Int (imul (qnum p) (qden q)) (imul (qnum q) (qden p))
  end
end

Frac : U is Quot QPair QRel end

dmul : Whole -> Whole -> Whole is
  fn (a : Whole) (b : Whole) is addW (mulW a (succ b)) b end
end

dmulSucc : (a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Eq Whole (mulW (succ a) (succ b)) (succ (dmul a b)) is
  fn (a : Whole) (b : Whole) is addWSuccR (mulW a (succ b)) b end
end

congE : (A : U) -> (B : U) -> (f : A -> B) -> (x : A) -> (y : A) -> Eq A x y -> Eq B (f x) (f y) is
  fn (A : U) (B : U) (f : A -> B) (x : A) (y : A) (p : Eq A x y) is
    subst A x y p (fn (z : A) is Eq B (f x) (f z) end) (refl (f x))
  end
end

monus : Whole -> Whole -> Whole is fn (a : Whole) (b : Whole) is subW a b end end

eqW : Whole -> Whole -> Bool is
  fn (m : Whole) (n : Whole) is
    case subW m n of
    | zero -> isZero (subW n m)
    | succ k -> false
    end
  end
end

cong : {A : U} -> {B : U} -> (f : A -> B) -> {x : A} -> {y : A} -> Eq A x y -> Eq B (f x) (f y) is
  fn {A : U} {B : U} (f : A -> B) {x : A} {y : A} (p : Eq A x y) is
    subst A x y p (fn (z : A) is Eq B (f x) (f z) end) refl
  end
end

sym : {A : U} -> {x : A} -> {y : A} -> Eq A x y -> Eq A y x is
  fn {A : U} {x : A} {y : A} (p : Eq A x y) is
    subst A x y p (fn (z : A) is Eq A z x end) refl
  end
end

trans : {A : U} -> {x : A} -> {y : A} -> {z : A} -> Eq A x y -> Eq A y z -> Eq A x z is
  fn {A : U} {x : A} {y : A} {z : A} (p : Eq A x y) (q : Eq A y z) is
    subst A y z q (fn (w : A) is Eq A x w end) p
  end
end

or : Bool -> Bool -> Bool is
  fn (a : Bool) (b : Bool) is
    BoolElim (fn (x : Bool) is Bool end) true b a
  end
end


-- ============================================================
-- THE ORD CLASSES. The ordering layer proper begins here: the Ordering
-- verdict type, DecEq and Ord as ops classes, the erased Le view, the
-- comparison defaults, and the two laws records.
-- ============================================================
data Ordering : U is
  lt : Ordering
| eq : Ordering
| gt : Ordering
end

flipOrd : Ordering -> Ordering is
  fn (o : Ordering) is
    OrderingElim (fn (x : Ordering) is Ordering end) gt eq lt o
  end
end

DecEq : U -> U is
  fn (A : U) is Sig (A -> A -> Bool) (fn (_e : A -> A -> Bool) is Bool end) end
end

mkDecEq : (A : U) -> (A -> A -> Bool) -> DecEq A is
  fn (A : U) (e : A -> A -> Bool) is
    Pair (A -> A -> Bool) (fn (_e : A -> A -> Bool) is Bool end) e true
  end
end

eqbOf : (A : U) -> DecEq A -> A -> A -> Bool is
  fn (A : U) (d : DecEq A) is d.1 end
end

Ord : U -> U is
  fn (A : U) is
    Sig (A -> A -> Bool) (fn (_le : A -> A -> Bool) is A -> A -> Ordering end)
  end
end

mkOrd : (A : U) -> (A -> A -> Bool) -> (A -> A -> Ordering) -> Ord A is
  fn (A : U) (le : A -> A -> Bool) (cmp : A -> A -> Ordering) is
    Pair (A -> A -> Bool) (fn (_le : A -> A -> Bool) is A -> A -> Ordering end) le cmp
  end
end

leOf : (A : U) -> Ord A -> A -> A -> Bool is
  fn (A : U) (o : Ord A) is o.1 end
end

compareOf : (A : U) -> Ord A -> A -> A -> Ordering is
  fn (A : U) (o : Ord A) is o.2 end
end

Le : (A : U) -> Ord A -> A -> A -> U is
  fn (A : U) (o : Ord A) (a : A) (b : A) is Eq Bool (leOf A o a b) true end
end

compareFromLe : (A : U) -> (A -> A -> Bool) -> A -> A -> Ordering is
  fn (A : U) (le : A -> A -> Bool) (a : A) (b : A) is
    let lab : Bool = le a b in
    let lba : Bool = le b a in
    case lab of
    | true  -> case lba of | true -> eq | false -> lt end
    | false -> gt
    end
  end
end

leFromCompare : (A : U) -> (A -> A -> Ordering) -> A -> A -> Bool is
  fn (A : U) (cmp : A -> A -> Ordering) (a : A) (b : A) is
    case cmp a b of
    | lt -> true
    | eq -> true
    | gt -> false
    end
  end
end

ge : (A : U) -> Ord A -> A -> A -> Bool is
  fn (A : U) (o : Ord A) (a : A) (b : A) is leOf A o b a end
end

ltB : (A : U) -> Ord A -> A -> A -> Bool is
  fn (A : U) (o : Ord A) (a : A) (b : A) is
    case leOf A o a b of
    | true  -> case leOf A o b a of | true -> false | false -> true end
    | false -> false
    end
  end
end

DecEqLaws : (A : U) -> DecEq A -> U is
  fn (A : U) (d : DecEq A) is
    And ((a : A) -> (b : A) -> Eq Bool (eqbOf A d a b) true -> Eq A a b)
        ((a : A) -> Eq Bool (eqbOf A d a a) true)
  end
end

OrdLaws : (A : U) -> Ord A -> U is
  fn (A : U) (o : Ord A) is
    And ((a : A) -> Le A o a a)
    (And ((a : A) -> (b : A) -> (c : A) -> Le A o a b -> Le A o b c -> Le A o a c)
    (And ((a : A) -> (b : A) -> Le A o a b -> Le A o b a -> Eq A a b)
    (And ((a : A) -> (b : A) -> Eq Bool (or (leOf A o a b) (leOf A o b a)) true)
    (And ((a : A) -> (b : A) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf A o a b) eq -> Eq A a b)
         ((a : A) -> (b : A) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf A o a b) lt -> Le A o a b)))))
  end
end

notEqOrd : Ordering -> Bool is
  fn (o : Ordering) is case o of | lt -> true | eq -> false | gt -> true end end
end

isGtOrd : Ordering -> Bool is
  fn (o : Ordering) is case o of | lt -> false | eq -> false | gt -> true end end
end

compareFromLeEq : (A : U) -> (le : A -> A -> Bool) -> (a : A) -> (b : A)
    -> Eq Ordering (compareFromLe A le a b) eq
    -> And (Eq Bool (le a b) true) (Eq Bool (le b a) true) is
  fn (A : U) (le : A -> A -> Bool) (a : A) (b : A)
     (h : Eq Ordering (compareFromLe A le a b) eq) is
    boolCaseEq (le a b)
      (fn (_g1 : Bool) is And (Eq Bool (le a b) true) (Eq Bool (le b a) true) end)
      (fn (e1 : Eq Bool (le a b) true) is
         boolCaseEq (le b a)
           (fn (_g2 : Bool) is And (Eq Bool (le a b) true) (Eq Bool (le b a) true) end)
           (fn (e2 : Eq Bool (le b a) true) is
              mkAnd (Eq Bool (le a b) true) (Eq Bool (le b a) true) e1 e2 end)
           (fn (e2 : Eq Bool (le b a) false) is
              let h1 : Eq Ordering
                  (case true of
                   | true  -> (case (le b a) of | true -> eq | false -> lt end)
                   | false -> gt
                   end) eq =
                subst Bool (le a b) true e1
                  (fn (w1 : Bool) is Eq Ordering
                     (case w1 of
                      | true  -> (case (le b a) of | true -> eq | false -> lt end)
                      | false -> gt
                      end) eq end)
                  h in
              let h2 : Eq Ordering lt eq =
                subst Bool (le b a) false e2
                  (fn (w2 : Bool) is Eq Ordering
                     (case w2 of | true -> eq | false -> lt end) eq end)
                  h1 in
              boolDiscTF (And (Eq Bool (le a b) true) (Eq Bool (le b a) true))
                (congE Ordering Bool notEqOrd lt eq h2)
            end)
       end)
      (fn (e1 : Eq Bool (le a b) false) is
         let hgt : Eq Ordering gt eq =
           subst Bool (le a b) false e1
             (fn (w1 : Bool) is Eq Ordering
                (case w1 of
                 | true  -> (case (le b a) of | true -> eq | false -> lt end)
                 | false -> gt
                 end) eq end)
             h in
         boolDiscTF (And (Eq Bool (le a b) true) (Eq Bool (le b a) true))
           (congE Ordering Bool notEqOrd gt eq hgt)
       end)
  end
end

compareFromLeLt : (A : U) -> (le : A -> A -> Bool) -> (a : A) -> (b : A)
    -> Eq Ordering (compareFromLe A le a b) lt
    -> Eq Bool (le a b) true is
  fn (A : U) (le : A -> A -> Bool) (a : A) (b : A)
     (h : Eq Ordering (compareFromLe A le a b) lt) is
    boolCaseEq (le a b)
      (fn (_g1 : Bool) is Eq Bool (le a b) true end)
      (fn (e1 : Eq Bool (le a b) true) is e1 end)
      (fn (e1 : Eq Bool (le a b) false) is
         let hgt : Eq Ordering gt lt =
           subst Bool (le a b) false e1
             (fn (w1 : Bool) is Eq Ordering
                (case w1 of
                 | true  -> (case (le b a) of | true -> eq | false -> lt end)
                 | false -> gt
                 end) lt end)
             h in
         boolDiscTF (Eq Bool (le a b) true)
           (congE Ordering Bool isGtOrd gt lt hgt)
       end)
  end
end

lteAbsurd : (a : Whole) -> (c : Whole) -> Eq Bool false true -> Eq Bool (leb a c) true is
  fn (a : Whole) (c : Whole) (h : Eq Bool false true) is
    subst Bool false true h
      (fn (z : Bool) is
         case z of
         | true  -> Eq Bool (leb a c) true
         | false -> Eq Bool true true
         end
       end)
      (refl true)
  end
end

lteAbsurdNat : (a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Eq Bool false true -> Eq Whole a b is
  fn (a : Whole) (b : Whole) (h : Eq Bool false true) is
    subst Bool false true h
      (fn (z : Bool) is
         case z of
         | true  -> Eq Whole a b
         | false -> Eq Whole a a
         end
       end)
      (refl a)
  end
end

lteAntisym : (a : Whole) -> (b : Whole)
   -> Eq Bool (leb a b) true -> Eq Bool (leb b a) true -> Eq Whole a b is
  fn (a : Whole) is
    WholeElim
      (fn (x : Whole) is
         (b : Whole)
           -> Eq Bool (leb x b) true -> Eq Bool (leb b x) true
           -> Eq Whole x b end)
      (fn (b : Whole) is
         WholeElim
           (fn (y : Whole) is
              Eq Bool (leb zero y) true -> Eq Bool (leb y zero) true
                -> Eq Whole zero y end)
           (fn (hab : Eq Bool (leb zero zero) true)
               (hba : Eq Bool (leb zero zero) true) is
              refl zero end)
           (fn (b' : Whole)
               (ihb : Eq Bool (leb zero b') true -> Eq Bool (leb b' zero) true
                        -> Eq Whole zero b') is
              fn (hab : Eq Bool (leb zero (succ b')) true)
                 (hba : Eq Bool false true) is
                lteAbsurdNat zero (succ b') hba end
            end)
           b
       end)
      (fn (a' : Whole)
          (ih : (b : Whole)
                  -> Eq Bool (leb a' b) true -> Eq Bool (leb b a') true
                  -> Eq Whole a' b) is
         fn (b : Whole) is
           WholeElim
             (fn (y : Whole) is
                Eq Bool (leb (succ a') y) true -> Eq Bool (leb y (succ a')) true
                  -> Eq Whole (succ a') y end)
             (fn (hab : Eq Bool false true)
                 (hba : Eq Bool (leb zero (succ a')) true) is
                lteAbsurdNat (succ a') zero hab end)
             (fn (b' : Whole)
                 (ihb : Eq Bool (leb (succ a') b') true
                          -> Eq Bool (leb b' (succ a')) true
                          -> Eq Whole (succ a') b') is
                fn (hab : Eq Bool (leb a' b') true)
                   (hba : Eq Bool (leb b' a') true) is
                  subst Whole a' b' (ih b' hab hba)
                    (fn (z : Whole) is Eq Whole (succ a') (succ z) end)
                    (refl (succ a'))
                end
              end)
             b
         end
       end)
      a
  end
end

lebTrans : (a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> (c : Whole)
    -> Eq Bool (leb a b) true -> Eq Bool (leb b c) true -> Eq Bool (leb a c) true is
  fn (a : Whole) is
    case a of
    | zero -> fn (b : Whole) (c : Whole) (hab : Eq Bool true true) (hbc : Eq Bool (leb b c) true) is
        refl true end
    | succ a2 with ih -> fn (b : Whole) is
        case b of
        | zero -> fn (c : Whole) (hab : Eq Bool false true) (hbc : Eq Bool (leb zero c) true) is
            lteAbsurd (succ a2) c hab end
        | succ b2 -> fn (c : Whole) is
            case c of
            | zero -> fn (hab : Eq Bool (leb a2 b2) true) (hbc : Eq Bool false true) is
                lteAbsurd (succ a2) zero hbc end
            | succ c2 -> fn (hab : Eq Bool (leb a2 b2) true) (hbc : Eq Bool (leb b2 c2) true) is
                ih b2 c2 hab hbc end
            end
          end
        end
      end
    end
  end
end

lebRefl : (a : Whole) -> Eq Bool (leb a a) true is
  fn (a : Whole) is
    case a of
    | zero -> refl true
    | succ k with ih -> ih
    end
  end
end

subSelf : (n : Whole) -> Eq Whole (subW n n) zero is
  fn (n : Whole) is
    WholeElim (fn (x : Whole) is Eq Whole (subW x x) zero end)
      (refl zero)
      (fn (k : Whole) (ih : Eq Whole (subW k k) zero) is trans (subWSucc k k) ih end)
      n
  end
end

eqWRefl : (n : Whole) -> Eq Bool (eqW n n) true is
  fn (n : Whole) is
    subst Whole zero (subW n n) (sym (subSelf n))
      (fn (z : Whole) is
         Eq Bool (case z of | zero -> isZero z | succ k -> false end) true
       end)
      (refl true)
  end
end

monusBothZeroEq : (x : Whole) -> (y : Whole)
    -> Eq Whole (subW x y) zero -> Eq Whole (subW y x) zero -> Eq Whole x y is
  fn (x : Whole) is
    WholeElim (fn (w : Whole) is
        (y : Whole) -> Eq Whole (subW w y) zero -> Eq Whole (subW y w) zero -> Eq Whole w y end)
      (fn (y : Whole) is
         case y of
         | zero -> fn (h1 : Eq Whole (subW zero zero) zero) (h2 : Eq Whole (subW zero zero) zero) is
             refl zero end
         | succ u -> fn (h1 : Eq Whole (subW zero (succ u)) zero) (h2 : Eq Whole (subW (succ u) zero) zero) is
             lteAbsurdNat zero (succ u)
               (subst Whole (succ u) zero h2
                  (fn (z : Whole) is Eq Bool (case z of | zero -> false | succ j -> true end) true end)
                  (refl true)) end
         end
       end)
      (fn (k : Whole) (ih : (y : Whole) -> Eq Whole (subW k y) zero -> Eq Whole (subW y k) zero -> Eq Whole k y) is
         fn (y : Whole) is
           case y of
           | zero -> fn (h1 : Eq Whole (subW (succ k) zero) zero) (h2 : Eq Whole (subW zero (succ k)) zero) is
               lteAbsurdNat (succ k) zero
                 (subst Whole (succ k) zero h1
                    (fn (z : Whole) is Eq Bool (case z of | zero -> false | succ j -> true end) true end)
                    (refl true)) end
           | succ u -> fn (h1 : Eq Whole (subW (succ k) (succ u)) zero) (h2 : Eq Whole (subW (succ u) (succ k)) zero) is
               cong (fn (z : Whole) is succ z end)
                 (ih u (trans (sym (subWSucc k u)) h1) (trans (sym (subWSucc u k)) h2)) end
           end
         end
       end)
      x
  end
end

eqWSound : (x : Whole) -> (y : Whole) -> Eq Bool (eqW x y) true -> Eq Whole x y is
  fn (x : Whole) (y : Whole) (h : Eq Bool (eqW x y) true) is
    WholeElim (fn (w : Whole) is Eq Whole (subW x y) w -> Eq Whole x y end)
      (fn (e1 : Eq Whole (subW x y) zero) is
         let h1 : Eq Bool (isZero (subW y x)) true =
           subst Whole (subW x y) zero e1
             (fn (z : Whole) is
                Eq Bool (case z of | zero -> isZero (subW y x) | succ k -> false end) true
              end)
             h in
         WholeElim (fn (v : Whole) is Eq Whole (subW y x) v -> Eq Whole x y end)
           (fn (e2 : Eq Whole (subW y x) zero) is monusBothZeroEq x y e1 e2 end)
           (fn (j : Whole) (ihj : Eq Whole (subW y x) j -> Eq Whole x y) is
              fn (e2 : Eq Whole (subW y x) (succ j)) is
                lteAbsurdNat x y
                  (subst Whole (subW y x) (succ j) e2
                     (fn (z : Whole) is Eq Bool (isZero z) true end)
                     h1)
              end
            end)
           (subW y x)
           (refl (subW y x))
       end)
      (fn (k : Whole) (ihk : Eq Whole (subW x y) k -> Eq Whole x y) is
         fn (e1 : Eq Whole (subW x y) (succ k)) is
           lteAbsurdNat x y
             (subst Whole (subW x y) (succ k) e1
                (fn (z : Whole) is
                   Eq Bool (case z of | zero -> isZero (subW y x) | succ kk -> false end) true
                 end)
                h)
         end
       end)
      (subW x y)
      (refl (subW x y))
  end
end


-- ============================================================
-- WHOLE INSTANCES. eqW gives DecEq; leb + compareFromLe gives Ord; the
-- six order laws are the leb corpus read off the nose.
-- ============================================================
instance decEqWhole : DecEq Whole is mkDecEq Whole eqW end

instance ordWhole   : Ord Whole   is mkOrd Whole leb (compareFromLe Whole leb) end

decEqLawsWhole : DecEqLaws Whole decEqWhole is
  mkAnd ((a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Eq Bool (eqbOf Whole decEqWhole a b) true -> Eq Whole a b)
        ((a : Whole) -> Eq Bool (eqbOf Whole decEqWhole a a) true)
    eqWSound
    eqWRefl
end

leTotalWhole : (a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Eq Bool (or (leb a b) (leb b a)) true is
  fn (a : Whole) (b : Whole) is
    boolCaseEq (leb a b)
      (fn (g : Bool) is Eq Bool (or g (leb b a)) true end)
      (fn (_e1 : Eq Bool (leb a b) true) is refl true end)
      (fn (e1 : Eq Bool (leb a b) false) is lebComplete a b e1 end)
  end
end

ordLawsWhole : OrdLaws Whole ordWhole is
  mkAnd ((a : Whole) -> Le Whole ordWhole a a)
    (And ((a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> (c : Whole) -> Le Whole ordWhole a b -> Le Whole ordWhole b c -> Le Whole ordWhole a c)
    (And ((a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Le Whole ordWhole a b -> Le Whole ordWhole b a -> Eq Whole a b)
    (And ((a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Eq Bool (or (leOf Whole ordWhole a b) (leOf Whole ordWhole b a)) true)
    (And ((a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Whole ordWhole a b) eq -> Eq Whole a b)
         ((a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Whole ordWhole a b) lt -> Le Whole ordWhole a b)))))
    lebRefl
    (mkAnd ((a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> (c : Whole) -> Le Whole ordWhole a b -> Le Whole ordWhole b c -> Le Whole ordWhole a c)
      (And ((a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Le Whole ordWhole a b -> Le Whole ordWhole b a -> Eq Whole a b)
      (And ((a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Eq Bool (or (leOf Whole ordWhole a b) (leOf Whole ordWhole b a)) true)
      (And ((a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Whole ordWhole a b) eq -> Eq Whole a b)
           ((a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Whole ordWhole a b) lt -> Le Whole ordWhole a b))))
      lebTrans
      (mkAnd ((a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Le Whole ordWhole a b -> Le Whole ordWhole b a -> Eq Whole a b)
        (And ((a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Eq Bool (or (leOf Whole ordWhole a b) (leOf Whole ordWhole b a)) true)
        (And ((a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Whole ordWhole a b) eq -> Eq Whole a b)
             ((a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Whole ordWhole a b) lt -> Le Whole ordWhole a b)))
        lteAntisym
        (mkAnd ((a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Eq Bool (or (leOf Whole ordWhole a b) (leOf Whole ordWhole b a)) true)
          (And ((a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Whole ordWhole a b) eq -> Eq Whole a b)
               ((a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Whole ordWhole a b) lt -> Le Whole ordWhole a b))
          leTotalWhole
          (mkAnd ((a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Whole ordWhole a b) eq -> Eq Whole a b)
                 ((a : Whole) -> (b : Whole) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Whole ordWhole a b) lt -> Le Whole ordWhole a b)
            (fn (a : Whole) (b : Whole) (h : Eq Ordering (compareOf Whole ordWhole a b) eq) is
               let pr : And (Eq Bool (leb a b) true) (Eq Bool (leb b a) true) =
                 compareFromLeEq Whole leb a b h in
               lteAntisym a b (pr.1) (pr.2)
             end)
            (fn (a : Whole) (b : Whole) (h : Eq Ordering (compareOf Whole ordWhole a b) lt) is
               compareFromLeLt Whole leb a b h
             end)))))
end


-- ============================================================
-- INT COMPARISON + INSTANCES. ileb compares by sign quadrant (negsucc
-- reverses), ieqb the diagonal; each law reduces its cases to Whole.
-- ============================================================
ileb : Int -> Int -> Bool is
  fn (x : Int) (y : Int) is
    case x of
    | nonneg a ->
        case y of
        | nonneg b  -> leb a b
        | negsucc j -> false
        end
    | negsucc k ->
        case y of
        | nonneg b  -> true
        | negsucc j -> leb j k
        end
    end
  end
end

ieqb : Int -> Int -> Bool is
  fn (x : Int) (y : Int) is
    case x of
    | nonneg a ->
        case y of
        | nonneg b  -> eqW a b
        | negsucc j -> false
        end
    | negsucc k ->
        case y of
        | nonneg b  -> false
        | negsucc j -> eqW k j
        end
    end
  end
end

ilebReflP : (a : Int) -> Eq Bool (ileb a a) true is
  fn (a : Int) is
    IntElim (fn (w : Int) is Eq Bool (ileb w w) true end)
      (fn (n : Whole) is lebRefl n end)
      (fn (k : Whole) is lebRefl k end)
      a
  end
end

ilebTransNonneg : (na : Whole) -> (b : Int) -> (c : Int)
    -> Eq Bool (ileb (nonneg na) b) true -> Eq Bool (ileb b c) true
    -> Eq Bool (ileb (nonneg na) c) true is
  fn (na : Whole) is
    IntElim (fn (wb : Int) is (c : Int)
        -> Eq Bool (ileb (nonneg na) wb) true -> Eq Bool (ileb wb c) true
        -> Eq Bool (ileb (nonneg na) c) true end)
      (fn (nb : Whole) is
        IntElim (fn (wc : Int) is
            Eq Bool (ileb (nonneg na) (nonneg nb)) true -> Eq Bool (ileb (nonneg nb) wc) true
            -> Eq Bool (ileb (nonneg na) wc) true end)
          (fn (nc : Whole) (h1 : Eq Bool (leb na nb) true) (h2 : Eq Bool (leb nb nc) true) is
            lebTrans na nb nc h1 h2 end)
          (fn (kc : Whole) (h1 : Eq Bool (leb na nb) true) (h2 : Eq Bool false true) is
            boolDiscTF (Eq Bool (ileb (nonneg na) (negsucc kc)) true)
              (symEq Bool false true h2) end)
       end)
      (fn (kb : Whole) (c : Int) (h1 : Eq Bool false true) (h2 : Eq Bool (ileb (negsucc kb) c) true) is
        boolDiscTF (Eq Bool (ileb (nonneg na) c) true) (symEq Bool false true h1) end)
  end
end

ilebTransNegsucc : (ka : Whole) -> (b : Int) -> (c : Int)
    -> Eq Bool (ileb (negsucc ka) b) true -> Eq Bool (ileb b c) true
    -> Eq Bool (ileb (negsucc ka) c) true is
  fn (ka : Whole) is
    IntElim (fn (wb : Int) is (c : Int)
        -> Eq Bool (ileb (negsucc ka) wb) true -> Eq Bool (ileb wb c) true
        -> Eq Bool (ileb (negsucc ka) c) true end)
      (fn (nb : Whole) is
        IntElim (fn (wc : Int) is
            Eq Bool (ileb (negsucc ka) (nonneg nb)) true -> Eq Bool (ileb (nonneg nb) wc) true
            -> Eq Bool (ileb (negsucc ka) wc) true end)
          (fn (nc : Whole) (h1 : Eq Bool true true) (h2 : Eq Bool (leb nb nc) true) is refl true end)
          (fn (kc : Whole) (h1 : Eq Bool true true) (h2 : Eq Bool false true) is
            boolDiscTF (Eq Bool (ileb (negsucc ka) (negsucc kc)) true)
              (symEq Bool false true h2) end)
       end)
      (fn (kb : Whole) is
        IntElim (fn (wc : Int) is
            Eq Bool (ileb (negsucc ka) (negsucc kb)) true -> Eq Bool (ileb (negsucc kb) wc) true
            -> Eq Bool (ileb (negsucc ka) wc) true end)
          (fn (nc : Whole) (h1 : Eq Bool (leb kb ka) true) (h2 : Eq Bool true true) is refl true end)
          (fn (kc : Whole) (h1 : Eq Bool (leb kb ka) true) (h2 : Eq Bool (leb kc kb) true) is
            lebTrans kc kb ka h2 h1 end)
       end)
  end
end

ilebTransP : (a : Int) -> (b : Int) -> (c : Int)
    -> Eq Bool (ileb a b) true -> Eq Bool (ileb b c) true -> Eq Bool (ileb a c) true is
  fn (a : Int) is
    IntElim (fn (wa : Int) is (b : Int) -> (c : Int)
        -> Eq Bool (ileb wa b) true -> Eq Bool (ileb b c) true -> Eq Bool (ileb wa c) true end)
      (fn (na : Whole) is ilebTransNonneg na end)
      (fn (ka : Whole) is ilebTransNegsucc ka end)
      a
  end
end

ilebAntisymP : (a : Int) -> (b : Int)
    -> Eq Bool (ileb a b) true -> Eq Bool (ileb b a) true -> Eq Int a b is
  fn (a : Int) is
    IntElim (fn (wa : Int) is (b : Int)
        -> Eq Bool (ileb wa b) true -> Eq Bool (ileb b wa) true -> Eq Int wa b end)
      (fn (na : Whole) is
        IntElim (fn (wb : Int) is
            Eq Bool (ileb (nonneg na) wb) true -> Eq Bool (ileb wb (nonneg na)) true
            -> Eq Int (nonneg na) wb end)
          (fn (nb : Whole) (h1 : Eq Bool (leb na nb) true) (h2 : Eq Bool (leb nb na) true) is
            congNonneg na nb (lteAntisym na nb h1 h2) end)
          (fn (kb : Whole) (h1 : Eq Bool false true) (h2 : Eq Bool true true) is
            boolDiscTF (Eq Int (nonneg na) (negsucc kb)) (symEq Bool false true h1) end)
       end)
      (fn (ka : Whole) is
        IntElim (fn (wb : Int) is
            Eq Bool (ileb (negsucc ka) wb) true -> Eq Bool (ileb wb (negsucc ka)) true
            -> Eq Int (negsucc ka) wb end)
          (fn (nb : Whole) (h1 : Eq Bool true true) (h2 : Eq Bool false true) is
            boolDiscTF (Eq Int (negsucc ka) (nonneg nb)) (symEq Bool false true h2) end)
          (fn (kb : Whole) (h1 : Eq Bool (leb kb ka) true) (h2 : Eq Bool (leb ka kb) true) is
            congNegsucc ka kb (symEq Whole kb ka (lteAntisym kb ka h1 h2)) end)
       end)
      a
  end
end

ilebTotalP : (a : Int) -> (b : Int) -> Eq Bool (or (ileb a b) (ileb b a)) true is
  fn (a : Int) is
    IntElim (fn (wa : Int) is (b : Int)
        -> Eq Bool (or (ileb wa b) (ileb b wa)) true end)
      (fn (na : Whole) is
        IntElim (fn (wb : Int) is
            Eq Bool (or (ileb (nonneg na) wb) (ileb wb (nonneg na))) true end)
          (fn (nb : Whole) is leTotalWhole na nb end)
          (fn (kb : Whole) is refl true end)
       end)
      (fn (ka : Whole) is
        IntElim (fn (wb : Int) is
            Eq Bool (or (ileb (negsucc ka) wb) (ileb wb (negsucc ka))) true end)
          (fn (nb : Whole) is refl true end)
          (fn (kb : Whole) is leTotalWhole kb ka end)
       end)
      a
  end
end

ieqbSoundP : (a : Int) -> (b : Int) -> Eq Bool (ieqb a b) true -> Eq Int a b is
  fn (a : Int) is
    IntElim (fn (wa : Int) is (b : Int) -> Eq Bool (ieqb wa b) true -> Eq Int wa b end)
      (fn (na : Whole) is
        IntElim (fn (wb : Int) is Eq Bool (ieqb (nonneg na) wb) true -> Eq Int (nonneg na) wb end)
          (fn (nb : Whole) (h : Eq Bool (eqW na nb) true) is
            congNonneg na nb (eqWSound na nb h) end)
          (fn (kb : Whole) (h : Eq Bool false true) is
            boolDiscTF (Eq Int (nonneg na) (negsucc kb)) (symEq Bool false true h) end)
       end)
      (fn (ka : Whole) is
        IntElim (fn (wb : Int) is Eq Bool (ieqb (negsucc ka) wb) true -> Eq Int (negsucc ka) wb end)
          (fn (nb : Whole) (h : Eq Bool false true) is
            boolDiscTF (Eq Int (negsucc ka) (nonneg nb)) (symEq Bool false true h) end)
          (fn (kb : Whole) (h : Eq Bool (eqW ka kb) true) is
            congNegsucc ka kb (eqWSound ka kb h) end)
       end)
      a
  end
end

ieqbReflP : (a : Int) -> Eq Bool (ieqb a a) true is
  fn (a : Int) is
    IntElim (fn (w : Int) is Eq Bool (ieqb w w) true end)
      (fn (n : Whole) is eqWRefl n end)
      (fn (k : Whole) is eqWRefl k end)
      a
  end
end

instance decEqInt : DecEq Int is mkDecEq Int ieqb end

instance ordInt   : Ord Int   is mkOrd Int ileb (compareFromLe Int ileb) end

decEqLawsInt : DecEqLaws Int decEqInt is
  mkAnd ((a : Int) -> (b : Int) -> Eq Bool (eqbOf Int decEqInt a b) true -> Eq Int a b)
        ((a : Int) -> Eq Bool (eqbOf Int decEqInt a a) true)
    ieqbSoundP
    ieqbReflP
end

ordLawsInt : OrdLaws Int ordInt is
  mkAnd ((a : Int) -> Le Int ordInt a a)
    (And ((a : Int) -> (b : Int) -> (c : Int) -> Le Int ordInt a b -> Le Int ordInt b c -> Le Int ordInt a c)
    (And ((a : Int) -> (b : Int) -> Le Int ordInt a b -> Le Int ordInt b a -> Eq Int a b)
    (And ((a : Int) -> (b : Int) -> Eq Bool (or (leOf Int ordInt a b) (leOf Int ordInt b a)) true)
    (And ((a : Int) -> (b : Int) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Int ordInt a b) eq -> Eq Int a b)
         ((a : Int) -> (b : Int) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Int ordInt a b) lt -> Le Int ordInt a b)))))
    ilebReflP
    (mkAnd ((a : Int) -> (b : Int) -> (c : Int) -> Le Int ordInt a b -> Le Int ordInt b c -> Le Int ordInt a c)
      (And ((a : Int) -> (b : Int) -> Le Int ordInt a b -> Le Int ordInt b a -> Eq Int a b)
      (And ((a : Int) -> (b : Int) -> Eq Bool (or (leOf Int ordInt a b) (leOf Int ordInt b a)) true)
      (And ((a : Int) -> (b : Int) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Int ordInt a b) eq -> Eq Int a b)
           ((a : Int) -> (b : Int) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Int ordInt a b) lt -> Le Int ordInt a b))))
      ilebTransP
      (mkAnd ((a : Int) -> (b : Int) -> Le Int ordInt a b -> Le Int ordInt b a -> Eq Int a b)
        (And ((a : Int) -> (b : Int) -> Eq Bool (or (leOf Int ordInt a b) (leOf Int ordInt b a)) true)
        (And ((a : Int) -> (b : Int) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Int ordInt a b) eq -> Eq Int a b)
             ((a : Int) -> (b : Int) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Int ordInt a b) lt -> Le Int ordInt a b)))
        ilebAntisymP
        (mkAnd ((a : Int) -> (b : Int) -> Eq Bool (or (leOf Int ordInt a b) (leOf Int ordInt b a)) true)
          (And ((a : Int) -> (b : Int) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Int ordInt a b) eq -> Eq Int a b)
               ((a : Int) -> (b : Int) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Int ordInt a b) lt -> Le Int ordInt a b))
          ilebTotalP
          (mkAnd ((a : Int) -> (b : Int) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Int ordInt a b) eq -> Eq Int a b)
                 ((a : Int) -> (b : Int) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Int ordInt a b) lt -> Le Int ordInt a b)
            (fn (a : Int) (b : Int) (h : Eq Ordering (compareOf Int ordInt a b) eq) is
               let pr : And (Eq Bool (ileb a b) true) (Eq Bool (ileb b a) true) =
                 compareFromLeEq Int ileb a b h in
               ilebAntisymP a b (pr.1) (pr.2)
             end)
            (fn (a : Int) (b : Int) (h : Eq Ordering (compareOf Int ordInt a b) lt) is
               compareFromLeLt Int ileb a b h
             end)))))
end

and : Bool -> Bool -> Bool is
  fn (a : Bool) (b : Bool) is BoolElim (fn (x : Bool) is Bool end) b false a end
end

boolDisjoint : (C : U) -> Eq Bool false true -> C is
  fn (C : U) (h : Eq Bool false true) is
    subst Bool false true h
      (fn (z : Bool) is
         case z of
         | true  -> C
         | false -> Eq Bool false false
         end
       end)
      (refl false)
  end
end

andTrueL : (a : Bool) -> (b : Bool) -> Eq Bool (and a b) true -> Eq Bool a true is
  fn (a : Bool) (b : Bool) (h : Eq Bool (and a b) true) is
    BoolElim (fn (x : Bool) is (Eq Bool (and x b) true -> Eq Bool x true) end)
      (fn (h1 : Eq Bool (and true b) true) is refl true end)
      (fn (h0 : Eq Bool (and false b) true) is h0 end)
      a h
  end
end

andTrueR : (a : Bool) -> (b : Bool) -> Eq Bool (and a b) true -> Eq Bool b true is
  fn (a : Bool) (b : Bool) (h : Eq Bool (and a b) true) is
    BoolElim (fn (x : Bool) is (Eq Bool (and x b) true -> Eq Bool b true) end)
      (fn (h1 : Eq Bool (and true b) true) is h1 end)
      (fn (h0 : Eq Bool (and false b) true) is boolDisjoint (Eq Bool b true) h0 end)
      a h
  end
end

andBoth : (a : Bool) -> (b : Bool) -> Eq Bool a true -> Eq Bool b true -> Eq Bool (and a b) true is
  fn (a : Bool) (b : Bool) (ha : Eq Bool a true) (hb : Eq Bool b true) is
    trans (cong (fn (z : Bool) is and z b end) ha) hb
  end
end


-- ============================================================
-- THE FRAC RESPECT PROOF. Positive-scaling monotonicity (lebMulPosR on
-- Whole, ilebMulPosR on Int) lets the cross-multiplication order descend
-- to the quotient. This is monotonicity, NOT cancellation.
-- ============================================================
lebAddSameL : (c : Whole) -> (x : Whole) -> (y : Whole) -> Eq Bool (leb (addW c x) (addW c y)) (leb x y) is
  fn (c : Whole) (x : Whole) (y : Whole) is
    WholeElim (fn (m : Whole) is Eq Bool (leb (addW m x) (addW m y)) (leb x y) end)
      (refl (leb x y))
      (fn (k : Whole) (ih : Eq Bool (leb (addW k x) (addW k y)) (leb x y)) is ih end)
      c
  end
end

lebMulPosR : (x : Whole) -> (y : Whole) -> (d : Whole) -> Eq Bool (leb (mulW x (succ d)) (mulW y (succ d))) (leb x y) is
  fn (x : Whole) (y : Whole) (d : Whole) is
    WholeElim (fn (m : Whole) is (n : Whole) -> Eq Bool (leb (mulW m (succ d)) (mulW n (succ d))) (leb m n) end)
      (fn (n : Whole) is refl (leb zero n) end)
      (fn (k : Whole) (ih : (n : Whole) -> Eq Bool (leb (mulW k (succ d)) (mulW n (succ d))) (leb k n)) is
         fn (n : Whole) is
           WholeElim (fn (nn : Whole) is Eq Bool (leb (mulW (succ k) (succ d)) (mulW nn (succ d))) (leb (succ k) nn) end)
             (subst Whole (succ (dmul k d)) (mulW (succ k) (succ d))
                (symEq Whole (mulW (succ k) (succ d)) (succ (dmul k d)) (dmulSucc k d))
                (fn (w : Whole) is Eq Bool (leb w zero) false end)
                (refl false))
             (fn (j : Whole) (ihj : Eq Bool (leb (mulW (succ k) (succ d)) (mulW j (succ d))) (leb (succ k) j)) is
                transEq Bool
                  (leb (addW (mulW k (succ d)) (succ d)) (addW (mulW j (succ d)) (succ d)))
                  (leb (addW (succ d) (mulW k (succ d))) (addW (succ d) (mulW j (succ d))))
                  (leb k j)
                  (transEq Bool
                     (leb (addW (mulW k (succ d)) (succ d)) (addW (mulW j (succ d)) (succ d)))
                     (leb (addW (succ d) (mulW k (succ d))) (addW (mulW j (succ d)) (succ d)))
                     (leb (addW (succ d) (mulW k (succ d))) (addW (succ d) (mulW j (succ d))))
                     (congE Whole Bool (fn (t : Whole) is leb t (addW (mulW j (succ d)) (succ d)) end)
                        (addW (mulW k (succ d)) (succ d)) (addW (succ d) (mulW k (succ d)))
                        (addWComm (mulW k (succ d)) (succ d)))
                     (congE Whole Bool (fn (t : Whole) is leb (addW (succ d) (mulW k (succ d))) t end)
                        (addW (mulW j (succ d)) (succ d)) (addW (succ d) (mulW j (succ d)))
                        (addWComm (mulW j (succ d)) (succ d))))
                  (transEq Bool
                     (leb (addW (succ d) (mulW k (succ d))) (addW (succ d) (mulW j (succ d))))
                     (leb (mulW k (succ d)) (mulW j (succ d)))
                     (leb k j)
                     (lebAddSameL (succ d) (mulW k (succ d)) (mulW j (succ d)))
                     (ih j))
              end)
             n
         end
       end)
      x y
  end
end

imulSwap3R : (a : Int) -> (b : Int) -> (c : Int) -> Eq Int (imul (imul a b) c) (imul (imul a c) b) is
  fn (a : Int) (b : Int) (c : Int) is
    transEq Int (imul (imul a b) c) (imul a (imul b c)) (imul (imul a c) b)
      (imulAssoc a b c)
      (transEq Int (imul a (imul b c)) (imul a (imul c b)) (imul (imul a c) b)
         (congImulR a (imul b c) (imul c b) (imulComm b c))
         (symEq Int (imul (imul a c) b) (imul a (imul c b)) (imulAssoc a c b)))
  end
end

congIleb2 : (u : Int) -> (u2 : Int) -> (v : Int) -> (v2 : Int)
    -> Eq Int u u2 -> Eq Int v v2 -> Eq Bool (ileb u v) (ileb u2 v2) is
  fn (u : Int) (u2 : Int) (v : Int) (v2 : Int) (eu : Eq Int u u2) (ev : Eq Int v v2) is
    transEq Bool (ileb u v) (ileb u2 v) (ileb u2 v2)
      (congE Int Bool (fn (t : Int) is ileb t v end) u u2 eu)
      (congE Int Bool (fn (t : Int) is ileb u2 t end) v v2 ev)
  end
end

imulNegPos : (j : Whole) -> (d : Whole) -> Eq Int (imul (negsucc j) (nonneg (succ d))) (negsucc (dmul j d)) is
  fn (j : Whole) (d : Whole) is
    subst Whole (succ (dmul j d)) (mulW (succ j) (succ d))
      (symEq Whole (mulW (succ j) (succ d)) (succ (dmul j d)) (dmulSucc j d))
      (fn (w : Whole) is Eq Int (ineg (nonneg w)) (negsucc (dmul j d)) end)
      (refl (negsucc (dmul j d)))
  end
end

ilebMulPosR : (a : Int) -> (b : Int) -> (d : Whole) -> Eq Bool (ileb (imul a (nonneg (succ d))) (imul b (nonneg (succ d)))) (ileb a b) is
  fn (a : Int) (b : Int) (d : Whole) is
    IntElim (fn (wa : Int) is Eq Bool (ileb (imul wa (nonneg (succ d))) (imul b (nonneg (succ d)))) (ileb wa b) end)
      (fn (x : Whole) is
         IntElim (fn (wb : Int) is Eq Bool (ileb (imul (nonneg x) (nonneg (succ d))) (imul wb (nonneg (succ d)))) (ileb (nonneg x) wb) end)
           (fn (y : Whole) is lebMulPosR x y d end)
           (fn (j : Whole) is
              subst Int (negsucc (dmul j d)) (imul (negsucc j) (nonneg (succ d)))
                (symEq Int (imul (negsucc j) (nonneg (succ d))) (negsucc (dmul j d)) (imulNegPos j d))
                (fn (z : Int) is Eq Bool (ileb (imul (nonneg x) (nonneg (succ d))) z) false end)
                (refl false)
            end)
           b
       end)
      (fn (k : Whole) is
         IntElim (fn (wb : Int) is Eq Bool (ileb (imul (negsucc k) (nonneg (succ d))) (imul wb (nonneg (succ d)))) (ileb (negsucc k) wb) end)
           (fn (y : Whole) is
              subst Int (negsucc (dmul k d)) (imul (negsucc k) (nonneg (succ d)))
                (symEq Int (imul (negsucc k) (nonneg (succ d))) (negsucc (dmul k d)) (imulNegPos k d))
                (fn (z : Int) is Eq Bool (ileb z (imul (nonneg y) (nonneg (succ d)))) true end)
                (refl true)
            end)
           (fn (j : Whole) is
              subst Int (negsucc (dmul k d)) (imul (negsucc k) (nonneg (succ d)))
                (symEq Int (imul (negsucc k) (nonneg (succ d))) (negsucc (dmul k d)) (imulNegPos k d))
                (fn (z : Int) is Eq Bool (ileb z (imul (negsucc j) (nonneg (succ d)))) (leb j k) end)
                (subst Int (negsucc (dmul j d)) (imul (negsucc j) (nonneg (succ d)))
                   (symEq Int (imul (negsucc j) (nonneg (succ d))) (negsucc (dmul j d)) (imulNegPos j d))
                   (fn (z : Int) is Eq Bool (ileb (negsucc (dmul k d)) z) (leb j k) end)
                   (transEq Bool
                      (leb (succ (dmul j d)) (succ (dmul k d)))
                      (leb (mulW (succ j) (succ d)) (mulW (succ k) (succ d)))
                      (leb j k)
                      (transEq Bool
                         (leb (succ (dmul j d)) (succ (dmul k d)))
                         (leb (mulW (succ j) (succ d)) (succ (dmul k d)))
                         (leb (mulW (succ j) (succ d)) (mulW (succ k) (succ d)))
                         (congE Whole Bool (fn (t : Whole) is leb t (succ (dmul k d)) end)
                            (succ (dmul j d)) (mulW (succ j) (succ d))
                            (symEq Whole (mulW (succ j) (succ d)) (succ (dmul j d)) (dmulSucc j d)))
                         (congE Whole Bool (fn (t : Whole) is leb (mulW (succ j) (succ d)) t end)
                            (succ (dmul k d)) (mulW (succ k) (succ d))
                            (symEq Whole (mulW (succ k) (succ d)) (succ (dmul k d)) (dmulSucc k d))))
                      (lebMulPosR (succ j) (succ k) d)))
            end)
           b
       end)
      a
  end
end

leRespR : (p : QPair) -> (q : QPair) -> (q' : QPair) -> QRel q q'
    -> Eq Bool (ileb (imul (qnum p) (qden q)) (imul (qnum q) (qden p)))
               (ileb (imul (qnum p) (qden q')) (imul (qnum q') (qden p))) is
  fn (p : QPair) (q : QPair) (q' : QPair) (h : QRel q q') is
    let np : Int = qnum p in
    let dp : Int = qden p in
    let nq : Int = qnum q in
    let dq : Int = qden q in
    let nq' : Int = qnum q' in
    let dq' : Int = qden q' in
    transEq Bool
      (ileb (imul np dq) (imul nq dp))
      (ileb (imul (imul np dq') dq) (imul (imul nq' dp) dq))
      (ileb (imul np dq') (imul nq' dp))
      (transEq Bool
         (ileb (imul np dq) (imul nq dp))
         (ileb (imul (imul np dq) dq') (imul (imul nq dp) dq'))
         (ileb (imul (imul np dq') dq) (imul (imul nq' dp) dq))
         (symEq Bool
            (ileb (imul (imul np dq) dq') (imul (imul nq dp) dq'))
            (ileb (imul np dq) (imul nq dp))
            (ilebMulPosR (imul np dq) (imul nq dp) (qdpred q')))
         (congIleb2 (imul (imul np dq) dq') (imul (imul np dq') dq)
                    (imul (imul nq dp) dq') (imul (imul nq' dp) dq)
            (imulSwap3R np dq dq')
            (transEq Int (imul (imul nq dp) dq') (imul (imul nq dq') dp) (imul (imul nq' dp) dq)
               (imulSwap3R nq dp dq')
               (transEq Int (imul (imul nq dq') dp) (imul (imul nq' dq) dp) (imul (imul nq' dp) dq)
                  (congImulL (imul nq dq') (imul nq' dq) dp h)
                  (imulSwap3R nq' dq dp)))))
      (ilebMulPosR (imul np dq') (imul nq' dp) (qdpred q))
  end
end

leRespL : (p : QPair) -> (p' : QPair) -> (q : QPair) -> QRel p p'
    -> Eq Bool (ileb (imul (qnum p) (qden q)) (imul (qnum q) (qden p)))
               (ileb (imul (qnum p') (qden q)) (imul (qnum q) (qden p'))) is
  fn (p : QPair) (p' : QPair) (q : QPair) (h : QRel p p') is
    let np : Int = qnum p in
    let dp : Int = qden p in
    let np' : Int = qnum p' in
    let dp' : Int = qden p' in
    let nq : Int = qnum q in
    let dq : Int = qden q in
    transEq Bool
      (ileb (imul np dq) (imul nq dp))
      (ileb (imul (imul np' dq) dp) (imul (imul nq dp') dp))
      (ileb (imul np' dq) (imul nq dp'))
      (transEq Bool
         (ileb (imul np dq) (imul nq dp))
         (ileb (imul (imul np dq) dp') (imul (imul nq dp) dp'))
         (ileb (imul (imul np' dq) dp) (imul (imul nq dp') dp))
         (symEq Bool
            (ileb (imul (imul np dq) dp') (imul (imul nq dp) dp'))
            (ileb (imul np dq) (imul nq dp))
            (ilebMulPosR (imul np dq) (imul nq dp) (qdpred p')))
         (congIleb2 (imul (imul np dq) dp') (imul (imul np' dq) dp)
                    (imul (imul nq dp) dp') (imul (imul nq dp') dp)
            (transEq Int (imul (imul np dq) dp') (imul (imul np dp') dq) (imul (imul np' dq) dp)
               (imulSwap3R np dq dp')
               (transEq Int (imul (imul np dp') dq) (imul (imul np' dp) dq) (imul (imul np' dq) dp)
                  (congImulL (imul np dp') (imul np' dp) dq h)
                  (imulSwap3R np' dp dq)))
            (imulSwap3R nq dp dp')))
      (ilebMulPosR (imul np' dq) (imul nq dp') (qdpred p))
  end
end


-- ------------------------------------------------------------
-- leF / eqF by double qlift, then the Frac instances and their six laws.
-- ------------------------------------------------------------
leFR : QPair -> Frac -> Bool is
  fn (p : QPair) is
    qlift QPair QRel Bool
      (fn (q : QPair) is ileb (imul (qnum p) (qden q)) (imul (qnum q) (qden p)) end)
      (fn (q : QPair) (q' : QPair) (r : QRel q q') is leRespR p q q' r end)
  end
end

leF : Frac -> Frac -> Bool is
  qlift QPair QRel (Frac -> Bool) leFR
    (fn (p : QPair) (p' : QPair) (r : QRel p p') is
      fn (z : Frac) is
        qind QPair QRel (fn (w : Frac) is Eq Bool (leFR p w) (leFR p' w) end)
          (fn (q : QPair) is leRespL p p' q r end)
          z
      end
    end)
end

eqF : Frac -> Frac -> Bool is
  fn (x : Frac) (y : Frac) is and (leF x y) (leF y x) end
end

instance decEqFrac : DecEq Frac is mkDecEq Frac eqF end

instance ordFrac   : Ord Frac   is mkOrd Frac leF (compareFromLe Frac leF) end

leReflF : (a : Frac) -> Le Frac ordFrac a a is
  fn (a : Frac) is
    qind QPair QRel (fn (w : Frac) is Eq Bool (leF w w) true end)
      (fn (p : QPair) is ilebReflP (imul (qnum p) (qden p)) end)
      a
  end
end

crossTransP : (p : QPair) -> (q : QPair) -> (r : QPair)
    -> Eq Bool (ileb (imul (qnum p) (qden q)) (imul (qnum q) (qden p))) true
    -> Eq Bool (ileb (imul (qnum q) (qden r)) (imul (qnum r) (qden q))) true
    -> Eq Bool (ileb (imul (qnum p) (qden r)) (imul (qnum r) (qden p))) true is
  fn (p : QPair) (q : QPair) (r : QPair)
     (h1 : Eq Bool (ileb (imul (qnum p) (qden q)) (imul (qnum q) (qden p))) true)
     (h2 : Eq Bool (ileb (imul (qnum q) (qden r)) (imul (qnum r) (qden q))) true) is
    let np : Int = qnum p in
    let dp : Int = qden p in
    let nq : Int = qnum q in
    let dq : Int = qden q in
    let nr : Int = qnum r in
    let dr : Int = qden r in
    let s1 : Eq Bool (ileb (imul (imul np dq) dr) (imul (imul nq dp) dr)) true =
      transEq Bool (ileb (imul (imul np dq) dr) (imul (imul nq dp) dr)) (ileb (imul np dq) (imul nq dp)) true
        (ilebMulPosR (imul np dq) (imul nq dp) (qdpred r))
        h1 in
    let s2raw : Eq Bool (ileb (imul (imul nq dr) dp) (imul (imul nr dq) dp)) true =
      transEq Bool (ileb (imul (imul nq dr) dp) (imul (imul nr dq) dp)) (ileb (imul nq dr) (imul nr dq)) true
        (ilebMulPosR (imul nq dr) (imul nr dq) (qdpred p))
        h2 in
    let s2 : Eq Bool (ileb (imul (imul nq dp) dr) (imul (imul nr dq) dp)) true =
      transEq Bool (ileb (imul (imul nq dp) dr) (imul (imul nr dq) dp)) (ileb (imul (imul nq dr) dp) (imul (imul nr dq) dp)) true
        (symEq Bool (ileb (imul (imul nq dr) dp) (imul (imul nr dq) dp)) (ileb (imul (imul nq dp) dr) (imul (imul nr dq) dp))
           (congIleb2 (imul (imul nq dr) dp) (imul (imul nq dp) dr) (imul (imul nr dq) dp) (imul (imul nr dq) dp)
              (imulSwap3R nq dr dp)
              (refl (imul (imul nr dq) dp))))
        s2raw in
    let s3 : Eq Bool (ileb (imul (imul np dq) dr) (imul (imul nr dq) dp)) true =
      ilebTransP (imul (imul np dq) dr) (imul (imul nq dp) dr) (imul (imul nr dq) dp) s1 s2 in
    let s4 : Eq Bool (ileb (imul (imul np dr) dq) (imul (imul nr dp) dq)) true =
      transEq Bool (ileb (imul (imul np dr) dq) (imul (imul nr dp) dq)) (ileb (imul (imul np dq) dr) (imul (imul nr dq) dp)) true
        (symEq Bool (ileb (imul (imul np dq) dr) (imul (imul nr dq) dp)) (ileb (imul (imul np dr) dq) (imul (imul nr dp) dq))
           (congIleb2 (imul (imul np dq) dr) (imul (imul np dr) dq) (imul (imul nr dq) dp) (imul (imul nr dp) dq)
              (imulSwap3R np dq dr)
              (imulSwap3R nr dq dp)))
        s3 in
    transEq Bool (ileb (imul np dr) (imul nr dp)) (ileb (imul (imul np dr) dq) (imul (imul nr dp) dq)) true
      (symEq Bool (ileb (imul (imul np dr) dq) (imul (imul nr dp) dq)) (ileb (imul np dr) (imul nr dp))
         (ilebMulPosR (imul np dr) (imul nr dp) (qdpred q)))
      s4
  end
end

leTransF : (a : Frac) -> (b : Frac) -> (c : Frac)
    -> Le Frac ordFrac a b -> Le Frac ordFrac b c -> Le Frac ordFrac a c is
  fn (a : Frac) (b : Frac) (c : Frac) (hab : Le Frac ordFrac a b) (hbc : Le Frac ordFrac b c) is
    qind QPair QRel
      (fn (wx : Frac) is (yy : Frac) -> (zz : Frac) -> Eq Bool (leF wx yy) true -> Eq Bool (leF yy zz) true -> Eq Bool (leF wx zz) true end)
      (fn (p : QPair) is
        fn (yy : Frac) is
          qind QPair QRel
            (fn (wy : Frac) is (zz : Frac) -> Eq Bool (leF (qin QPair QRel p) wy) true -> Eq Bool (leF wy zz) true -> Eq Bool (leF (qin QPair QRel p) zz) true end)
            (fn (q : QPair) is
              fn (zz : Frac) is
                qind QPair QRel
                  (fn (wz : Frac) is Eq Bool (leF (qin QPair QRel p) (qin QPair QRel q)) true -> Eq Bool (leF (qin QPair QRel q) wz) true -> Eq Bool (leF (qin QPair QRel p) wz) true end)
                  (fn (r : QPair) is
                    fn (g1 : Eq Bool (leF (qin QPair QRel p) (qin QPair QRel q)) true) (g2 : Eq Bool (leF (qin QPair QRel q) (qin QPair QRel r)) true) is
                      crossTransP p q r g1 g2
                    end
                   end)
                  zz
              end
            end)
            yy
        end
      end)
      a b c hab hbc
  end
end

leAntisymF : (a : Frac) -> (b : Frac)
    -> Le Frac ordFrac a b -> Le Frac ordFrac b a -> Eq Frac a b is
  fn (a : Frac) (b : Frac) (hab : Le Frac ordFrac a b) (hba : Le Frac ordFrac b a) is
    qind QPair QRel
      (fn (wx : Frac) is (yy : Frac) -> Eq Bool (leF wx yy) true -> Eq Bool (leF yy wx) true -> Eq Frac wx yy end)
      (fn (p : QPair) is
        fn (yy : Frac) is
          qind QPair QRel
            (fn (wy : Frac) is Eq Bool (leF (qin QPair QRel p) wy) true -> Eq Bool (leF wy (qin QPair QRel p)) true -> Eq Frac (qin QPair QRel p) wy end)
            (fn (q : QPair) is
              fn (g1 : Eq Bool (leF (qin QPair QRel p) (qin QPair QRel q)) true) (g2 : Eq Bool (leF (qin QPair QRel q) (qin QPair QRel p)) true) is
                qsound QPair QRel p q
                  (ilebAntisymP (imul (qnum p) (qden q)) (imul (qnum q) (qden p)) g1 g2)
              end
            end)
            yy
        end
      end)
      a b hab hba
  end
end

leTotalF : (a : Frac) -> (b : Frac)
    -> Eq Bool (or (leOf Frac ordFrac a b) (leOf Frac ordFrac b a)) true is
  fn (a : Frac) (b : Frac) is
    qind QPair QRel
      (fn (wx : Frac) is (yy : Frac) -> Eq Bool (or (leOf Frac ordFrac wx yy) (leOf Frac ordFrac yy wx)) true end)
      (fn (p : QPair) is
        fn (yy : Frac) is
          qind QPair QRel
            (fn (wy : Frac) is Eq Bool (or (leOf Frac ordFrac (qin QPair QRel p) wy) (leOf Frac ordFrac wy (qin QPair QRel p))) true end)
            (fn (q : QPair) is ilebTotalP (imul (qnum p) (qden q)) (imul (qnum q) (qden p)) end)
            yy
        end
      end)
      a b
  end
end

ordLawsFrac : OrdLaws Frac ordFrac is
  mkAnd ((a : Frac) -> Le Frac ordFrac a a)
    (And ((a : Frac) -> (b : Frac) -> (c : Frac) -> Le Frac ordFrac a b -> Le Frac ordFrac b c -> Le Frac ordFrac a c)
    (And ((a : Frac) -> (b : Frac) -> Le Frac ordFrac a b -> Le Frac ordFrac b a -> Eq Frac a b)
    (And ((a : Frac) -> (b : Frac) -> Eq Bool (or (leOf Frac ordFrac a b) (leOf Frac ordFrac b a)) true)
    (And ((a : Frac) -> (b : Frac) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Frac ordFrac a b) eq -> Eq Frac a b)
         ((a : Frac) -> (b : Frac) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Frac ordFrac a b) lt -> Le Frac ordFrac a b)))))
    leReflF
    (mkAnd ((a : Frac) -> (b : Frac) -> (c : Frac) -> Le Frac ordFrac a b -> Le Frac ordFrac b c -> Le Frac ordFrac a c)
      (And ((a : Frac) -> (b : Frac) -> Le Frac ordFrac a b -> Le Frac ordFrac b a -> Eq Frac a b)
      (And ((a : Frac) -> (b : Frac) -> Eq Bool (or (leOf Frac ordFrac a b) (leOf Frac ordFrac b a)) true)
      (And ((a : Frac) -> (b : Frac) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Frac ordFrac a b) eq -> Eq Frac a b)
           ((a : Frac) -> (b : Frac) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Frac ordFrac a b) lt -> Le Frac ordFrac a b))))
      leTransF
      (mkAnd ((a : Frac) -> (b : Frac) -> Le Frac ordFrac a b -> Le Frac ordFrac b a -> Eq Frac a b)
        (And ((a : Frac) -> (b : Frac) -> Eq Bool (or (leOf Frac ordFrac a b) (leOf Frac ordFrac b a)) true)
        (And ((a : Frac) -> (b : Frac) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Frac ordFrac a b) eq -> Eq Frac a b)
             ((a : Frac) -> (b : Frac) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Frac ordFrac a b) lt -> Le Frac ordFrac a b)))
        leAntisymF
        (mkAnd ((a : Frac) -> (b : Frac) -> Eq Bool (or (leOf Frac ordFrac a b) (leOf Frac ordFrac b a)) true)
          (And ((a : Frac) -> (b : Frac) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Frac ordFrac a b) eq -> Eq Frac a b)
               ((a : Frac) -> (b : Frac) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Frac ordFrac a b) lt -> Le Frac ordFrac a b))
          leTotalF
          (mkAnd ((a : Frac) -> (b : Frac) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Frac ordFrac a b) eq -> Eq Frac a b)
                 ((a : Frac) -> (b : Frac) -> Eq Ordering (compareOf Frac ordFrac a b) lt -> Le Frac ordFrac a b)
            (fn (a : Frac) (b : Frac) (h : Eq Ordering (compareOf Frac ordFrac a b) eq) is
               let pr : And (Eq Bool (leF a b) true) (Eq Bool (leF b a) true) =
                 compareFromLeEq Frac leF a b h in
               leAntisymF a b (pr.1) (pr.2)
             end)
            (fn (a : Frac) (b : Frac) (h : Eq Ordering (compareOf Frac ordFrac a b) lt) is
               compareFromLeLt Frac leF a b h
             end)))))
end

decEqLawsFrac : DecEqLaws Frac decEqFrac is
  mkAnd ((a : Frac) -> (b : Frac) -> Eq Bool (eqbOf Frac decEqFrac a b) true -> Eq Frac a b)
        ((a : Frac) -> Eq Bool (eqbOf Frac decEqFrac a a) true)
    (fn (a : Frac) (b : Frac) (h : Eq Bool (eqbOf Frac decEqFrac a b) true) is
       leAntisymF a b (andTrueL (leF a b) (leF b a) h) (andTrueR (leF a b) (leF b a) h)
     end)
    (fn (a : Frac) is andBoth (leF a a) (leF a a) (leReflF a) (leReflF a) end)
end


-- A closing exercise: compareOf on the Whole instance evaluates the
-- three-way view through the compareFromLe default. 2 <= 3 and not 3 <= 2,
-- so the verdict is lt.
main : Ordering is compareOf Whole ordWhole (succ (succ zero)) (succ (succ (succ zero))) end
